%20Moss%20(L)%2C%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20(R).%3Cp%3EDimitrios%20Kambouris%2FWireImage%20for%20Vogue%20via%20Getty%20Images%2C%20Justin%20Sullivan%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20Group%20cofounders%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20conspiring%20to%20dilute%20their%20shares.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20Litinsky%20and%20Wes%20Moss%2C%20former%20contestants%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%2C%26quot%3B%20pitched%20the%20venture%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20could%20complicate%20an%20upcoming%20shareholder%20vote%20on%20a%20merger%20that%20would%20take%20the%20company%20public.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20cofounders%20of%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20media%20company%20have%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20claiming%20executives%20at%20the%20company%20schemed%20to%20deprive%20them%20of%20shares%20that%20could%20be%20worth%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20ahead%20of%20a%20possible%20merger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Litinsky%20and%20Wes%20Moss%2C%20who%20met%20Trump%20when%20they%20were%20contestants%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%2C%26quot%3B%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20through%20their%20partnership%2C%20United%20Atlantic%20Ventures%20(UAV).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20suit%2C%20seen%20by%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20they%20claimed%20executives%2C%20including%20Trump%2C%20were%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2F02%2F29%2Ftruth-social-lawsuit-trump-media-founders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3B11th%20hour%2C%20pre-merger%20corporate%20maneuvering%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20dilute%20their%20stake%20in%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20Media's%20press%20office%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20was%20made%20outside%20of%20regular%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20is%20the%20latest%20of%20three%20that%20could%20complicate%20an%20upcoming%20shareholder%20vote%20on%20a%20long-pending%20merger%20that%20would%20take%20the%20company%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bid%20would%20see%20Trump's%20company%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20his%20social%20media%20network%20Truth%20Social%2C%20merge%20with%20blank-check%20company%20Digital%20World%20Acquisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELitinsky%20and%20Moss%20first%20came%20to%20Trump%20in%202021%20with%20a%20pitch%20for%20a%20Trump-branded%20media%20startup%20after%20he%20was%20barred%20from%20Twitter%2C%20and%20they%20agreed%20on%20a%20deal%20that%20gave%20Trump%20a%2090%25%20stake%20and%20UAV%208.6%25%2C%20per%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20lawsuit%20claims%20that%20Trump%20and%20other%20leaders%20sought%20to%20increase%20the%20amount%20of%20authorized%20stock%20from%20120%20million%20shares%20to%201%20billion%20shares%2C%20which%20would%20reduce%20Litinsky%20and%20Moss'%20stake%20to%20less%20than%201%25%20ahead%20of%20the%20merger%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20filing%20from%20Digital%20World%2C%20Trump's%20shares%20would%20be%20worth%20more%20than%20%243%20billion%20after%20the%20merger%20at%20Thursday's%20stock%20price%2C%20while%20UAV's%20stake%20would%20be%20worth%20nearly%20%24300%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sum%20would%20be%20a%20welcome%20financial%20boost%20for%20the%20former%20president%2C%20who%20faces%20huge%20legal%20costs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F02%2F25%2Ftrump-354-million-penalty-judgment%2F%3Fitid%3Dlk_inline_manual_25%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20%24450%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20also%20claims%20that%20the%20Trump%20Media%20board%20planned%20to%20give%20new%20shares%20to%20%26quot%3BTrump%20and%2For%20his%20associates%20and%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20previously%20reported%20that%20Trump%20had%20called%20Litinsky%20in%20October%202021%20to%20ask%20if%20he%20would%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2022%2F10%2F15%2Ftruth-social-trump-animosity-whistleblower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20give%20up%20some%20of%20his%20shares%20to%20Trump's%20wife%2C%20Melania%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20he%20had%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELitinsky%20and%20Moss%20left%20Trump%20Media%20soon%20after%20UAV%20launched%20the%20business%20after%20a%20dispute%20with%20company%20leaders%2C%20but%20they%20retained%20their%20shares%2C%20per%20the%20Digital%20World%20SEC%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two-year%20attempted%20merger%20between%20Trump%20Media%20and%20Digital%20World%20Acquisition%20Corp%20has%20faced%20ongoing%20delays%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20SEC%20investigations%20into%20potential%20securities%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20final%20shareholder%20vote%20on%20March%2022%2C%20the%20merger%20still%20faces%20complications%20as%20legal%20hurdles%20continue%20to%20mount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-company-cofounders-sue-scheme-dilute-shares-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709403161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e32ab8ce7f1785b2e5b437%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-company-cofounders-sue-scheme-dilute-shares-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andy%20Litinsky%20and%20Wes%20Moss%2C%20who%20met%20Trump%20when%20they%20were%20contestants%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%2C%26quot%3B%20filed%20the%20lawsuit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-company-cofounders-sue-scheme-dilute-shares-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22