resence%20of%20Amit%20Shah.%20I%20heartily%20welcome%20his%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%20family.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20you%20will%20make%20an%20important%20contribution%20to%20the%20journey%20towards%20a%20developed%20India%20and%20the%20development%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%3Cem%3EAb%20ki%20baar%20NDA%20400%20paar.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERumours%20that%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RLD%20was%20in%20the%20works%20had%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20a%20while%20and%20had%20got%20credence%20when%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20was%20announced%20for%20Mr%20Chaudhary's%20grandfather%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20on%20February%209.%20The%20RLD%20chief%20had%20welcomed%20the%20honour%2C%20writing%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EDil%20jeet%20liya%20mera%3C%2Fem%3E%20(They%20have%20won%20my%20heart).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20reporters%20had%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20was%20going%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20anything%20left%3F%20How%20can%20I%20refuse%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20he%20had%20indicated%20that%20the%20deal%20with%20the%20BJP%20had%20been%20sealed%20and%20a%20formal%20announcement%20could%20be%20expected%20soon.%20On%20questions%20that%20people%20in%20his%20party%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20decision%2C%20the%20RLD%20chief%20had%20said%20he%20had%20made%20it%20only%20after%20speaking%20to%20everyone%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoll%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%20is%20the%20second%20party%20to%20leave%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20after%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20Janata%20Dal%20United.%20And%20while%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leader%20may%20not%20have%20the%20same%20profile%20as%20the%20JDU%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20its%20exit%20will%20be%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20opposition%20because%20it%20is%20a%20player%20in%20the%20all-important%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%2062%20in%202019%20-%20which%20was%20nine%20lower%20than%20it%20had%20got%20in%202014%20-%20but%20still%20managed%20to%20get%20to%20a%20tally%20of%20303%20nationally.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20targeting%20winning%20370%20on%20its%20own%20and%20400%20for%20the%20NDA.%20The%20RLD%2C%20which%20enjoys%20support%20among%20the%20Jats%2C%20can%20play%20a%20role%20in%20getting%20it%20closer%20to%20that%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20list%20of%20195%20candidates%20issued%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20named%2051%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20has%20been%20speculated%20that%20the%20RLD%20will%20contest%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20get%20two%20ministerial%20berths%20in%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709400180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F63b5qv38_jp-nadda-jayant-chaudhary_625x300_02_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjayant-chaudharys-rashtriya-lok-dal-formally-joins-bjp-led-nda-alliance-5164381%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20a%20day%20that%20the%20BJP%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%20195%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20led%20by%20the%20party%20also%20got%20a%20boost%20with%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20formally%20joining%20the%20bloc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjayant-chaudharys-rashtriya-lok-dal-formally-joins-bjp-led-nda-alliance-5164381%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjayant-chaudharys-rashtriya-lok-dal-formally-joins-bjp-led-nda-alliance-5164381%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjayant-chaudharys-rashtriya-lok-dal-formally-joins-bjp-led-nda-alliance-5164381%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20Spotlights%20%26quot%3BTareekh%20Pe%20Tareekh%26quot%3B%20Syndrome%20In%20Judicial%20System%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20that%20adjournment%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20judicial%20system%20is%20disheartening%2C%20underlined%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20on%20Saturday%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20prolongs%20the%20agony%20of%20litigants%20and%20perpetuates%20the%20cycle%20of%20backlog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20major%20issues%20is%20that%20of%20%26quot%3Badjournment%20culture.%26quot%3B%20This%20practice%2C%20characterized%20by%20repeated%20requests%20for%20delays%20in%20proceedings%2C%20has%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20the%20efficiency%20and%20integrity%20of%20our%20legal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20addressing%20the%20All%20India%20District%20Judges%20Conference%20at%20Dhordo%20in%20Gujarat's%20Kutch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20adjournment%20and%20tareekh%20pe%20tareekh%20prolongs%20the%20agony%20of%20litigants.%20Common%20citizen%20feels%20that%20adjournment%20is%20part%20of%20judicial%20process%20and%20my%20experience%20is%20that%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20decide%20a%20complex%20case%20with%20a%20judgment%20than%20to%20persuade%20a%20lawyer%20to%20argue%20a%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20expressed%20concern%20that%20the%20longstanding%20principle%20of%20%26quot%3Bbail%20is%20the%20rule%2C%20jail%20is%20the%20exception%26quot%3B%20is%20losing%20ground%20with%20district%20courts%20hesitating%20to%20deal%20with%20matters%20involving%20personal%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20a%20victim%20of%20sexual%20assault%20whose%20case%20remains%20unresolved%20in%20the%20courts%20for%20several%20years.%20Isn't%20this%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20access%20justice%3F%20The%20concept%20of%20access%20to%20justice%20should%20extend%20beyond%20mere%20access%20to%20the%20courts%3B%20it%20should%20also%20guarantee%20that%20citizens%20receive%20timely%20judgments%20from%20courts%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20even%20one%20adjournment%20might%20look%20like%20a%20routine%20affair%2C%20it%20can%20have%20severe%20ramifications%20for%20the%20litigants%2C%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOften%2C%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20legal%20battle%20never%20comes%20to%20light%20during%20the%20farmer's%20lifetime.%20Instead%2C%20the%20burden%20falls%20upon%20their%20legal%20heirs%2C%20who%20find%20themselves%20embroiled%20in%20protracted%20legal%20proceedings%20long%20after%20their%20loved%20one's%20passing.%20We%20should%20not%20wait%20for%20our%20citizens%20to%20die%20for%20their%20case%20to%20be%20decided%20by%20a%20court%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourts%20nationwide%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20noted%2C%20are%20grappling%20with%20a%20significant%20backlog%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Balarming%20level%20of%20pending%20cases%26quot%3B.%20This%20backlog%20and%20pendency%20of%20cases%20present%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20efficient%20administration%20of%20justice%20and%20the%20timely%20resolution%20of%20legal%20disputes%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAddressing%20the%20backlog%20and%20pendency%20of%20cases%20requires%20a%20multi-faceted%20approach%20encompassing%20systemic%20reforms%2C%20procedural%20enhancements%2C%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20technological%20solutions.%20Efforts%20to%20streamline%20court%20procedures%2C%20expedite%20case%20disposal%2C%20and%20promote%20alternative%20dispute%20resolution%20mechanisms%20can%20help%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20on%20the%20judicial%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20can%20be%20a%20great%20tool%20for%20improving%20efficiency%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20sunshine%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20best%20disinfectant%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20technology%20is%20the%20best%20tool%20at%20our%20disposal%20to%20eliminate%20the%20inefficiency%20and%20opacity%20surrounding%20judicial%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20diversity%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20much%20improvement%20has%20been%20made%20towards%20achieving%20greater%20gender%20representation%20with%20women%20now%20constituting%2036.3%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20working%20strength%20of%20the%20district%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20while%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20in%20terms%20of%20gender%20representation%2C%20there%20remains%20a%20pressing%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20judicial%20institutions%20are%20truly%20inclusive%20and%20accommodating%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudges%20should%20not%20be%20unduly%20affected%20by%20criticism%20and%20commentary%20on%20social%20media%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20times%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20noticeable%20increase%20in%20judges%20facing%20criticisms%20and%20commentary%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%20And%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20I%20have%20had%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20scrutiny%20too!%20Even%20if%20I%20say%20just%20a%20single%20word%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20get%20reported%20faster%20than%20a%20speeding%20bullet.%20But%2C%20should%20we%2C%20judges%2C%20be%20unduly%20affected%20by%20this%3F%20The%20role%20of%20a%20judge%20is%20to%20dispense%20justice%20impartially%2C%20without%20being%20swayed%20by%20external%20pressures%20or%20public%20opinions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709399880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbo0hsb0o_chief-justice-1200_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-spotlights-adjournment-culture-in-judicial-system-5164549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20perception%20that%20adjournment%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20judicial%20system%20is%20disheartening%2C%20underlined%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20on%20Saturday%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20prolongs%20the%20agony%20of%20litigants%20and%20perpetuates%20the%20cycle%20of%20backlog.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-spotlights-adjournment-culture-in-judicial-system-5164549%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-spotlights-adjournment-culture-in-judicial-system-5164549%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-spotlights-adjournment-culture-in-judicial-system-5164549%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rihanna%20came%20out%20of%20retirement%20for%20the%20Ambani%20wedding%20concert%20and%20a%20hefty%20payday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rihanna%20performs%20onstage%20during%20the%2095th%20Annual%20Academy%20Awards%20at%20Dolby%20Theatre%20on%20March%2012%2C%202023%20in%20Hollywood%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e3578190413ab8e1d8a19a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223090%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERihanna%2C%20photographed%20performing%20at%20the%2095th%20Annual%20Academy%20Awards%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Winter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%