their%20home's%20doorstep%2C%20applied%20tilak%20on%20his%20forehead%20and%20garlanded%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20performed%20'%3Cem%3Eaarti%3C%2Fem%3E'%20-%20a%20ritual%20of%20welcoming%20guests%20by%20offering%20blessings%20-%20and%20touched%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20BJP%20leader%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20to%20contest%20from%20MP's%20Vidhisha%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20wife%20welcomes%20him%20home%20by%20putting%20a%20'Tilak'%20on%20his%20forehead%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20his%20candidature%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20in%20Bhopal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSEc9gjHZ8J%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSEc9gjHZ8J%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1763924399814586737%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20first%20list%20of%2024%20candidates%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20featured%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20while%20Bhopal%20MP%20Pragya%20Singh%20Thakur%20was%20replaced%20by%20another%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20to%20the%20central%20leadership%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%2C%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20(Shah)%20ji%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20(Singh)%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2064-year-old%2C%20who%20led%20the%20BJP%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20last%20year's%20assembly%20elections%20yet%20was%20replaced%20by%20Mohan%20Yadav%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20would%20be%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20nearly%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20new%20role%20assigned%20to%20him%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20like%20my%20mother%2C%20my%20mission.%20Whatever%20role%20was%20given%20to%20me%2C%20I%20will%20fulfill%20it%20with%20dedication%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20insisted%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20if%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20chances%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20asserted%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Broadmap%20for%20Vidisha%20is%20ready%26quot%3B%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20close%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Vidisha%2C%20we%20are%20like%20family.%20The%20roadmap%20for%20Vidisha%20is%20ready%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20will%20win%20all%2029%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20state%20will%20put%2029%20garlands%20on%20PM%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20represented%20Vidisha%20-%20a%20seat%20represented%20by%20BJP%20stalwarts%20like%20late%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20(1991)%20and%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20(2009%20and%202014)%2C%20and%20newspaper%20publisher%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20(1971)%20-%20five%20times%20before%20becoming%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20November%202005.%20He%20is%20currently%20MLA%20from%20the%20Budhni%20assembly%20segment%20which%20falls%20under%20the%20Vidisha%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20the%20candidates'%20list%2C%20terming%20it%20%26quot%3Bbalanced%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20balanced%20list%20with%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%2053%2C%20was%20fielded%20from%20Guna%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20where%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20lost%20to%20BJP's%20KP%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20candidate%20from%20Chhindwara.%20There%20was%20speculation