irstrike%20hit%20a%20tent%20in%20Rafah%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%2C%20in%20an%20area%20where%20people%20are%20seeking%20sanctuary%20from%20Israel's%20devastating%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%20another%2050%20people%20were%20wounded%20in%20the%20strike%20next%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20Tel%20Al-Sultan%20area%20of%20Rafah.%20One%20of%20the%20dead%20was%20a%20medic%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strike%20hit%20one%20tent%2C%20where%20people%20took%20shelter%2C%20directly%2C%20shrapnel%20came%20inside%20the%20hospital%20where%20me%20and%20friends%20were%20sitting%2C%20we%20survived%20by%20a%20miracle%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20witness%20told%20Reuters%20by%20phone%20from%20the%20area%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20its%20forces%20killed%20eight%20militants%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20around%2020%20militants%20in%20the%20central%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20three%20more%20in%20Rimal%2C%20near%20Gaza%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostilities%20came%20amid%20uncertainty%20over%20whether%20negotiations%20on%20a%20Gaza%20ceasefire%20would%20resume%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%20over%20a%20million%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20the%20Rafah%20area%2C%20fleeing%20the%20Israeli%20offensive%20which%20has%20laid%20waste%20to%20much%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20killing%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20health%20authorities%20in%20Hamas-run%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20launched%20the%20offensive%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%2C%20in%20which%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Israel%20and%20another%20253%20abducted%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20said%20he%20hopes%20a%20ceasefire%20will%20be%20in%20place%20by%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Muslim%20fasting%20month%20of%20Ramadan%2C%20which%20starts%20on%20March%2010.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20Friday%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20there%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20pressure%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20has%20grown%2C%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20warning%20that%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20population%20of%202.3%20million%20people%20are%20one%20step%20away%20from%20famine%20in%20the%20territory%20blockaded%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20people%20searching%20for%20food%20in%20farmland%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%20area%20of%20Beit%20Hanoun%20on%20Saturday%20were%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20residents%20and%20medics%20said.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirteen%20children%20have%20died%20at%20the%20Kamal%20Adwan%20hospital%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20in%20the%20last%20three%20days%20from%20dehydration%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Ministry%20of%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20at%20the%20hospital%20said%20more%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20dying.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20child%20is%20supposed%20to%20eat%20three%20meals%20a%20day%20and%20he%20only%20eats%20one%2C%20he%20obviously%20suffers%20from%20malnutrition%2C%20and%20all%20the%20diseases%20that%20come%20because%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doctor%20Imad%20Dardonah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20announced%20on%20Friday%20plans%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20first%20military%20airdrop%20of%20food%20and%20supplies%20into%20Gaza%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20Palestinians%20queuing%20for%20aid%20drew%20renewed%20attention%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20authorities%20in%20Gaza%20said%20115%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Thursday's%20incident%2C%20attributing%20the%20deaths%20to%20Israeli%20fire%20and%20calling%20it%20a%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20disputed%20those%20figures%20and%20said%20most%20victims%20were%20trampled%20or%20run%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECEASEFIRE%20TALKS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20have%20been%20negotiating%20via%20mediators%20including%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20Egyptian%20security%20sources%20said%20Israeli%20and%20Hamas%20delegations%20were%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20Cairo%20on%20Sunday%20to%20resume%20indirect%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20Israeli%20report%20cast%20doubt%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20Israel%20or%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Egyptian%20sources%20said%20the%20parties%20had%20agreed%20on%20the%20duration%20of%20a%20Gaza%20truce%2C%20as%20well%20as%20hostage%20and%20prisoner%20releases%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20deal%20still%20requires%20an%20agreement%20on%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20from%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20a%20return%20of%20its%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Israel's%20Ynet%20news%2C%20citing%20an%20unnamed%20senior%20official%2C%20reported%20that%20Israel%20would%20not%20be%20sending%20a%20delegation%20to%20the%20Cairo%20talks%20until%20it%20received%20a%20full%20list%20of%20hostages%20held%20in%20Gaza%20who%20were%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20central%20issue%20being%20worked%20on%20was%20how%20many%20hostages%20would%20be%20released%20from%20Gaza%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20how%20many%20Palestinians%20would%20be%20freed%20by%20Israel%20in%20exchange%20for%20each%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20clear%20answers%20are%20given%2C%20a%20delegation%20would%20not%20be%20leaving%20to%20Cairo%2C%26quot%3B%20Ynet%20cited%20the%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Palestinian%20official%20familiar%20wi