2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20Kishan%2C%20who%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20the%20Gorakhpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20during%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20has%20been%20nominated%20once%20more%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Transitioning%20from%20an%20actor%20to%20a%20politician%2C%20Ravi%20Kishan%20is%20now%20recognized%20as%20the%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20of%20Bhojpuri%20cinema.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20he%20has%20indeed%20made%20a%20significant%20mark%20in%20the%20pan-Indian%20entertainment%20industry.%20Ravi%20Kishan%20has%20acted%20in%20numerous%20Hindi%2C%20Tamil%2C%20and%20Telugu%20films%2C%20earning%20recognition%20for%20his%20performances.%20Apart%20from%20his%20work%20in%20films%2C%20Ravi%20Kishan%20has%20also%20ventured%20into%20the%20digital%20streaming%20space%20on%20several%20popular%20web%20services%20on%20OTT%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20secured%20victories%20in%20the%20North-East%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20both%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections%2C%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20speculation%20regarding%20a%20potential%20shift%20to%20contest%20from%20a%20seat%20in%20Bihar.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20been%20confirmed%20that%20he%20will%2C%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time%2C%20vie%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20North-East%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinesh%20Lal%20Yadav%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20'Nirahua%2C'%20contested%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20the%20Azamgarh%20constituency%20in%202019%2C%20where%20he%20faced%20a%20defeat%20against%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20national%20president%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20However%2C%20in%20the%202022%20elections%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20decided%20to%20contest%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20Subsequently%2C%20a%20by-election%20was%20conducted%20to%20fill%20the%20vacant%20position%2C%20and%20Nirahua%20eme