0brother%20Anant%20Ambani's%20pre-wedding%20celebrations%2C%20Isha%20Ambani%20took%20center%20stage%20to%20deliver%20a%20sweet%20speech%2C%20expressing%20gratitude%20to%20the%20guests%20and%20sharing%20heartfelt%20sentiments%20as%20the%20Ambani%20family%20prepares%20to%20welcome%20Anant's%20bride-to-be%20Radhika%20Merchant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fisha-ambanis-heartwarming-speech-at-anant-ambanis-pre-wedding-bash%2Farticleshow%2F108167069.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Police%20Submits%20Closure%20Report%20In%20Cheating%20Case%20Against%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Citing%20%26quot%3BMistake%20of%20Facts%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11103455%2FF5k08sFWsAAr9LD.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMumbai%3A%20After%20accusing%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20leader%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20of%20cheating%20and%20criminal%20breach%20of%20trust%20in%20the%20alleged%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20scam%20at%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Cooperative%20Bank%20(MSCB)%2C%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20of%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20now%20claimed%20that%20a%20criminal%20case%20was%20filed%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20mistake%20of%20facts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20March%201%2C%20the%20EOW%20filed%20a%20%E2%80%98C%20summary%E2%80%99%20report%20before%20the%20special%20court%20in%20Mumbai.%20A%20%E2%80%98C%20summary%E2%80%99%20report%20is%20filed%20when%20the%20investigating%20agency%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20a%20person%20is%20wrongly%20implicated%20in%20a%20case%20due%20to%20mistake%20of%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20then%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20court%20before%20the%20case%20is%20closed%20against%20the%20person.%20The%20report%20was%20filed%20through%20special%20public%20prosecutor%20Raja%20Thackery.%20Special%20judge%20R.N.%20Rokade%20of%20Mumbai%20sessions%20court%20has%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20until%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20take%20the%20final%20call%20on%20whether%20to%20accept%20the%20closure%20report%20or%20to%20direct%20the%20police%20to%20conduct%20further%20investigation%20and%20subsequently%20file%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%E2%80%99s%20move%20is%20not%20surprising.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20pattern%20in%20both%20the%20state%20and%20central%20agencies%E2%80%99%20conduct%20in%20cases%20involving%20leaders%2C%20more%20specifically%20of%20those%20from%20the%20opposition%20who%20have%20jumped%20ships%20to%20join%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20or%20form%20an%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20EOW%20has%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20the%20matter.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tri-party%20government%20comprising%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%94%20was%20in%20power%2C%20the%20EOW%20had%20first%20filed%20a%20closure%20report.%20Pawar%20was%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20even%20then.%20The%20closure%20report%20was%20against%20Pawar%20and%2070%20others%20named%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20the%20MVA%20government%20collapsed%20in%20the%20state%20and%20BJP%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20took%20over%2C%20the%20EOW%20had%20suddenly%20shown%20interest%20in%20%E2%80%9Creinvestigating%E2%80%9D%20the%20matter.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20the%20EOW%20had%20said%20that%20it%20would%20want%20to%20further%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-2024-elections-near-ed-accelerates-actions-against-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3E%20As%202024%20Elections%20Near%2C%20ED%20Accelerates%20Actions%20Against%20Opposition%20Leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20months%2C%20Pawar%20had%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20became%20the%20second%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20July%202023%2C%20with%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20already%20holding%20that%20post.%20For%20this%2C%20Pawar%20had%20parted%20ways%20with%20his%20uncle%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20NCP%20party%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20several%20other%20MLAs%20left.%20Recently%2C%20the%20election%20commission%20granted%20him%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol%2C%20forcing%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20rename%20his%20party%20as%20NCP-Sharadchandra%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20published%20a%20detailed%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20suddenly%20all%20allegations%20against%20them%20were%20either%20dropped%20or%20the%20state%20machinery%20had%20lost%20interest%20in%20investigating%20the%20matter%20any%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%20alone%20some%20eight%20leaders%20have%20either%20left%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20or%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20or%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20fearing%20adverse%20action%20against%20them.%20Each%20of%20them%20are%20facing%20investigation%20either%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Department%20(ED)%20or%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAjit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20case%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW%E2%80%99s%20case%20dates%20back%20to%202019%20when%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20had%20ordered%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter%20following%20a%20petition.%20The%20EOW%20filed%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20in%20the%20case%20and%20all%20accused%20were%20booked%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%20406%20(criminal%20breach%20of%20trust)%20and%20420%20(cheating)%2C%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%20and%20Securitisation%20and%20Reconstruction%20of%20Financial%20Assets%20and%20Enforcement%20of%20Security%20Interest%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20loans%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20were%20obtained%20by%20sugar%20cooperatives%2C%20spinning%20mills%20and%20other%20entities%20from%20district%20and%20cooperative%20banks%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20allegedly%20had%20direct%20link%20as%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20directors%20of%20the%20MSC%20bank%20then.%20The%20loans%20were%20allegedly%20procured%20through%20illegal%20means%20and%20the%20EOW%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20many%20irregularities%20in%20the%20procurement%20process.%20According%20to%20the%20EOW%E2%80%99s%20FIR%2C%20the%20state%20exchequer%20suffered%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20between%20January%201%2C%202007%2C%20and%20December%2031%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20filed%20a%20separate%20offence%20alleging%20money-laundering%20based%20on%20the%20EOW%E2%80%99s%20case.%20It%20has%20so%20far%20filed%20two%20chargesheets%2C%20including%20against%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20faction%20MLA%20Prajakt%20Tanpure.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20base%20offence%2C%20like%20the%20EOW%20case%2C%20the%20ED%20cannot%20continue%20with%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709395229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11103455%2FF5k08sFWsAAr9LD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmumbai-police-scraps-cheating-case-against-ajit-pawar-citing-mistake-of-facts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20series%20of%20coincidences%2C%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20having%20central%20agencies%20chasing%20them%20and%20then%20when%20they%20defect%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20pursuit%20appears%20to%20stop.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmumbai-police-scraps-cheating-case-against-ajit-pawar-citing-mistake-of-facts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20cordless%20vacuum%20review%3A%20A%20thoughtfully%20designed%20vacuum%20with%20powerful%20cleaning%20but%20a%20premium%20price%20tag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20and%20cleaning%20in%20action%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de590f6080194819fa9e7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYour%20floors%20may%20look%20clean%2C%20but%20the%20premium%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20is%20here%20to%20tackle%20what%20the%20eye%20can't%20see%2C%20with%20improved%20design%20features%2C%20plus%20the%20brand's%20most%20powerful%20suction%20and%20longest%20battery%20life%20yet.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%20or%20so%2C%20Dyson%20comes%20out%20with%20its%20latest%20and%20greatest%20vacuum%20cleaner%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20version%20being%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-64457-20%26h%3D6e26db2acab5fd9e9142f2970df8ed5f1d7044a8bb4c435a65a098533b6bf8fb%26postID%3D65de27462b09cffef0610378%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-gen5detect-cordless-vacuum-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D16190%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.dyson.com%25252Fvacuum-cleaners%25252Fcordless%25252Fgen5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDyson%20Gen5Detect%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20new%20and%20improved%20machine%20to%20the%20line%20up%20comes%20with%20all%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20and%20boasts%20Dyson's%20longest%20battery%20life%2C%20Dyson's%20strongest%20suction%20power%2C%20and%20HEPA%20filtration.%20But%20is%20that%20enough%20to%20justify%20its%20eye-watering%20%24950%20price%20tag%20%E2%80%94%20and%20over%20%241%2C050%20if%20you%20choose%20their%20large-home%20Outsize%20model%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20tested%20much%20of%20the%20Dyson%20lineup%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20a%20vacuum%20cleaner%20at%20this%20price%20point%20will%20definitely%20be%20scrutinized.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20flawless%3B%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20this%20latest%20version%20is.%20A%20Business%20Insider%20reporter%20identified%20it%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-status-symbols-popular-this-year-2024-1%23forget-the-dyson-airwrap-2024-is-all-about-the-dyson-gen5outsize-vacuum-11%5C%22%3EQuiet%20Status%20Symbols%20of%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20another%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-home-products-worth-splurging-on-2024-1%5C%22%3Eluxury%20home%20product%20worth%20splurging%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20premium%20price%20tag%20or%20not%2C%20it's%20destined%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20coveted%20Dyson%20innovation.%20On%20TikTok%20alone%2C%20the%20hashtags%20for%20the%20Detect%20and%20Outsize%20models%20have%20racked%20up%20nearly%20125%20million%20views.%20Social%20media%20videos%20and%20status%20symbols%20aside%2C%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20will%20literally%20make%20you%20want%20to%20clean%20%E2%80%94%20either%20for%20the%20satisfying%20gratification%20of%20noticeably%20cleaner%20floors%20or%20the%20pure%20realization%20of%20how%20dirty%20your%20floors%20really%20were.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20put%20into%20perspective%20with%20my%20favorite%20Dyson%20vacuum%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-64457-20%26h%3D28df03b658b3dfd78845d21dde6590b3be40288ba270c6e835a8ac38f2ee4339%26postID%3D65de27462b09cffef0610378%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-gen5detect-cordless-vacuum-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D16190%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.dyson.com%25252Fvacuum-cleaners%25252Fcordless%25252Fv15%25252Fdetect-yellow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDyson%20V15%20Detect%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20operates%20about%2010%20minutes%20longer%20and%20only%20has%20a%20marginally%20stronger%20suction%20%E2%80%94%20262%20air%20watts%20(AW)%20versus%20240%20AW.%20The%20average%20person%20probably%20won't%20notice%20these%20improvements.%20The%20biggest%20upgrades%20and%20reasons%20to%20splurge%20are%20the%20heightened%20HEPA%20filtration%2C%20power-button%20operation%20(as%20opposed%20to%20a%20trigger)%2C%20and%20the%20built-in%20crevice%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20get%20into%20the%20details%20about%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20use%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20cordless%20vacuum%20at%20home.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%20and%20design%5C%22%3ESetup%20and%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20parts%20assembled%20on%20the%20floor%20in%20a%20flatlay%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de4d22ce7f1785b2e44f89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%202%20cleaner%20heads%2C%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20comes%20with%20a%20mini-motorized%20tool%2C%20dusting%20brush%2C%20and%20a%20built-in%20crevice%20tool.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20vacuum%20parts%20come%20expertly%20wrapped%20in%20cardboard%20and%20paper.%20The%20handheld%20unit%20holds%20the%20main%20technological%20components%20of%20the%20vacuum%2C%20including%20the%20brushless%20Hyperdymium%20motor%20that%20spins%20at%20135%2C000%20revolutions%20per%20a%20minute%20(rpm)%2C%20fully-sealed%20HEPA%20filtration%2C%20a%20Piezo%20sensor%2C%20and%20Dyson%20Dynamic%20Load%20Sensing%20(DLS)%2C%20which%20automatically%20adjusts%20power%20to%20different%20floor%20types%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20dust%20being%20collected.%20The%20LCD%20displays%20an%20accurate%20measurement%20of%20the%20runtime%20and%20a%20real-time%20indicator%20of%20the%20amount%20and%20size%20of%20particles%20being%20collected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gen5Detect%20includes%20two%20cleaner%20heads.%20The%20signature%20Digital%20Motorbar%20cleaner%20head%20for%20carpet%20and%20hard%20floor%20cleaning%20uses%20stiff%20nylon%20brushes%20to%20dig%20into%20carpets%20and%20has%20hair%20removal%20vanes%20that%20automatically%20clear%20hair%20from%20the%20brush%20bar.%20The%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20is%20a%20soft%20brush%20featuring%20Dyson's%20proprietary%20green%20laser%20for%20hard%20floors%20that%20reveals%20dust%20and%20dirt%20undetectable%20to%20the%20eye.%20This%20next-gen%20of%20the%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20is%20said%20to%20have%20a%20laser%20that%20produces%20twice%20the%20brightness%20for%20better%20visibility%20from%20the%20original%20design%20found%20on%20the%20V15%20Detect%20and%20V12%20Detect%20Slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223542%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20gen5detect%20(right)%20and%20v15%20detect%20(left)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de54b790413ab8e1d74351%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20placed%20the%20Gen5Detect%20side%20by%20side%20with%20my%20V15%20Detect%2C%20and%20the%20Gen5Detect%20(right)%20was%20clearly%20brighter.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20wand%20is%20a%20built-in%20crevice%20tool%2C%20which%20is%20convenient%20%E2%80%94%20one%20less%20tool%20to%20have%20to%20store%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20did%20find%20myself%20occasionally%20reaching%20to%20unsnap%20that%20part%20when%20I%20meant%20to%20detach%20the%20longer%20wand%20to%20prepare%20to%20eject%20the%20dustbin.%20For%20accessories%2C%20you'll%20find%20a%20combination%20brush%20and%20hair%20screw%20tool%2C%20which%20is%20a%20great%20mini-motorized%20device%20for%20cleaning%20upholstery%20and%20small%20areas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20wall%20docking%20station%20and%20a%20charger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5%20Detect%20Vacuum%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5%20Detect%20Vacuum%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20green%20laser%20off%20and%20on%20with%20the%20dyson%20gen5detect%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de4d6290413ab8e1d73ea6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20my%20dog%20can't%20believe%20the%20difference%20the%20green%20laser%20on%20the%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20makes%20at%20showcasing%20the%20accumulated%20dust%20under%20the%20chair.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EOverall%20ease%20of%20use%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gen5Detect%20is%20a%20joy%20to%20use.%20It's%20lightweight%20and%20highly%20maneuverable%2C%20and%20the%20transition%20to%20a%20power%20button%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20trigger%2C%20makes%20it%20comfortable%20to%20hold.%20The%20button%20is%20placed%20in%20a%20way%20on%20the%20head%2C%20however%2C%20that%20requires%20two-handed%20operation%3A%20your%20dominant%20hand%20for%20supporting%20the%20vacuum%20and%20your%20other%20for%20powering%20it%20on%20and%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20laser%20design%2C%20the%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20what%20your%20eye%20is%20blind%20to%20in%20natural%20light%E2%80%A6%20it's%20both%20alarming%20and%20reassuring%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20before%20and%20after%20of%20how%20well%20the%20vacuum%20picks%20up%20dirt%20and%20dust.%20I've%20noticed%20it's%20easier%20to%20see%20the%20hidden%20dirt%20on%20wood%20flooring%20than%20on%20light-colored%20tile%2C%20and%20the%20laser%20reveals%20dirt%20best%20in%20lower%20light%20conditions%20than%20in%20direct%20sunlight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECleaning%20performance%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dyson%20gen5detect%20cleans%20sugar%20on%20a%20wood%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de4e136080194819fa97f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20reveals%20what%20the%20eye%20can't%20see%2C%20including%20the%20microscopic%20flecks%20of%20sugar%20that%20were%20pushed%20forward%20and%20promptly%20suctioned%20up.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20the%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20reveals%20what%20the%20eye%20can't%20see%20is%20only%20part%20of%20why%20the%20cleaner%20head%20works%20well%3B%20it%20also%20cleans%20delicate%20hard%20floor%20types%20with%20its%20soft%20roller%20design.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20not%20tough%20on%20dirt%20because%20once%20you%20pull%20back%2C%20the%20floor%20is%20spotless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwapping%20to%20the%20Digital%20Motorbar%20cleaner%20head%20for%20my%20carpeted%20landing%20(about%20a%2025%20sq.%20ft.%20area)%2C%20the%20dustbin%20filled%20with%20dirt%20and%20debris%20in%20moments.%20This%20was%20before%20I%20even%20made%20it%20further%20down%20the%20hallway.%20I%20noticed%20that%20hair%20did%20wrap%20along%20the%20cleaner%20head%2C%20but%20as%20I%20cleaned%20further%2C%20the%20hair%20unwound%20itself%3B%20it%20just%20required%20extra%20revolutions%20of%20the%20brush%20roll.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20carpet%20in%20this%20hallway%20is%20also%20easily%2030-plus%20years%20old%20and%20not%20as%20taut%20in%20some%20places.%20At%20some%20angles%20of%20holding%20the%20vacuum%2C%20I%20noticed%20it%20lost%20suction%20and%20needed%20to%20be%20turned%20on%20and%20off%20again.%20At%20first%2C%20this%20was%20a%20little%20annoying%2C%20but%20the%20solution%20is%20easy.%20The%20Motorbar%20has%20an%20adjustable%20gate%20that%20affects%20suction%20but%20lets%20larger%20pieces%20of%20debris%20pass%2C%20and%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20carpet%2C%20it%20helps%20it%20glide%20easier%20when%20put%20on%20the%20minus%20(-)%20setting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dyson%20Gen5detect%20cleaning%20a%20window%20frame%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de4e47ce7f1785b2e4505d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20conveniently%20built-in%20dusting%20brush%20and%20crevice%20tool%20means%20one%20less%20attachment%20to%20look%20after.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20transitioned%20to%20handheld%20cleaning%2C%20the%20conveniently%20built-in%20crevice%20tool%20means%20one%20less%20attachment%20I%20have%20to%20keep%20on%20hand%20or%20nearby%2C%20while%20the%20mini%20hair%20screw%20tool%20visibly%20brightens%20up%20upholstery%20such%20as%20a%20dog%20bed%20or%20the%20sofa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20standardized%20tests%20that%20we%20put%20all%20vacuums%20we%20test%20through%2C%20both%20cleaner%20heads%20expertly%20chomped%20through%20big%20debris%20like%20Cheerios%20(previously%2C%20I've%20had%20issues%20with%20earlier%20versions%20of%20the%20Motorbar%20simply%20pushing%20large%20debris%20forward).%20With%20flour%2C%20the%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20picked%20up%20100%25%20of%20the%20flour%20and%20the%20Motorbar%20picked%20up%2096%25%20on%20carpets%20and%20hard%20floors.%20Of%20note%2C%20the%20flour%20coated%20the%20interior%20sides%20of%20the%20cleaner%20head%2C%20which%20means%20more%20might%20have%20been%20suctioned%20from%20the%20carpet%2C%20just%20residue%20was%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20observation%20from%20my%20testing%3A%20the%20Fluffy%20Optic%20cleaner%20head%20adjusted%20itself%20into%20boost%20mode%20to%20suction%20up%20all%20the%20coffee%20grounds%2C%20while%20the%20green%20laser%20showed%20how%20little%20flecks%20of%20sugar%20and%20rice%20were%20scattered%20forward%20from%20the%20sheer%20power%20of%20the%20vacuum%20but%20still%20easily%20picked%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDustbin%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gen5Detect%20employs%20the%20same%20emptying%20technique%20as%20is%20predecessors%20and%20requires%20you%20to%20detach%20the%20handheld%20from%20the%20stick%20wand.%20The%20dustbin%20ejects%20into%20your%20trash%20receptacle%20with%20a%20lever.%20Most%20of%20the%20collected%20debris%20hygienically%20falls%20out%2C%20but%20if%20you%20overfill%20the%20bin%20past%20the%20max%20fill%20line%2C%20you%20may%20find%20yourself%20needing%20to%20stick%20your%20hand%20up%20in%20the%20bin%20to%20loosen%20out%20dust%20that%20gets%20caught.%20Sometimes%2C%20hair%20also%20wraps%20around%20the%20shaft%2C%20which%20requires%20manual%20removal%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20far%20easier%20to%20remove%20than%20getting%20stuck%20on%20a%20brush%20roll.%20Honestly%2C%20I've%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20bagless%20vacuum%20that%20hasn't%20required%20some%20manual%20removal%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time%20to%20remove%20clingy%20pieces%20of%20dust%20and%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EMaintenance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20requires%20little%20maintenance.%20In%20case%20of%20a%20blockage%20or%20the%20filter%20needs%20to%20be%20cleaned%2C%20the%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20will%20update%20you%20on%20its%20LCD%20screen.%20The%20HEPA%20filter%2C%20as%20are%20the%20brush%20rolls%2C%20is%20washable%2C%20though%20you%20will%20want%20to%20wait%2024%20hours%20for%20them%20to%20dry%20before%20putting%20them%20back%20into%20the%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBattery%20life%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20LCD%20Screen%20and%20power%20button%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de500f90413ab8e1d74013%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20LCD%20screen%20shows%20the%20battery%20runtime%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20dust%20and%20the%20size%20collected.%20The%20one-touch%20power%20button%20is%20also%20located%20directly%20next%20to%20it.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gen5Detect%20advertises%20up%20to%2070%20minutes%20of%20battery%20life%2C%20and%20I%20never%20ran%20into%20any%20issues%20running%20short%20on%20time%20when%20I%20took%20the%20vacuum%20through%20my%20house.%20I%20probably%20averaged%20at%20least%2045%20minutes%20of%20cleaning%20time%20per%20session.%20Cleaning%20on%20hard%20floors%20versus%20carpets%20offered%20longer%20battery%20life%2C%20as%20it%20required%20less%20suction%20power.%20Rarely%20did%20I%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20activate%20boost%20mode%2C%20if%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EFiltration%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDyson's%20whole-machine%20HEPA%20filtration%20is%20a%20fully-sealed%20filtration%20system%20that%20traps%20and%20seals%20in%20microscopic%20dust%2C%20expelling%20cleaner%20air.%20It%20uses%20cyclone%20technology%20to%20spin%20air%20to%20separate%20particles%20from%20airflow%2C%20without%20a%20loss%20in%20suction.%20According%20to%20a%20Dyson%20press%20release%2C%20the%20vacuums%20use%201.9m%20of%20filter%20media%20folded%20145%20times%20to%20trap%2099.99%25%20of%20particles%20down%20to%200.1%20microns%2C%20and%20the%20filter%20was%20also%20specially%20tested%20on%20live%20viruses%20to%20ensure%2099.9%25%20removal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dyson%20Gen5Detect%20is%20wildly%20expensive%2C%20creeping%20to%20over%20%241%2C000%20when%20you%20add%20tax%2C%20making%20this%20one%20very%20expensive%20vacuum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20performance%20issue%20that%20I%20ran%20into%20was%20that%20on%20the%20carpet%2C%20it%20was%20a%20little%20more%20stop-and-go%20as%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20hold%20it%20at%20the%20right%20angle%20to%20get%20maximum%20airflow.%20Once%20I%20sorted%20out%20the%20suction%20levels%2C%20I%20was%20on%20my%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Dyson's%20top-of-the-line%20model%2C%20the%20Gen5Detect%20is%20also%20available%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-64457-20%26h%3D8a4aef9310e7b422a56be0390e9eff306f3aa6f787bf571f9c6e4084db8c1263%26postID%3D65de27462b09cffef0610378%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-gen5detect-cordless-vacuum-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D16190%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.dyson.com%25252Fvacuum-cleaners%25252Fcordless%25252Fgen5%25252Foutsize-hepa-absolute-prussian-blue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOutsize%3C%2Fa%3E%20edition%20for%20%24100%20more%2C%20which%20features%20a%20half-gallon%20dustbin%20for%20extended%20cleaning%20without%20pausing%20to%20empty%20the%20bin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3