ual%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighly%20skilled%20work%20in%20healthcare%20and%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20maths%20(STEM)%20will%20increase%20in%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Ffeatured-insights%2Fmckinsey-explainers%2Fwhat-is-the-future-of-work%5C%22%3EE-commerce%2C%20the%20green%20economy%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0remote%20working%20culture%2C%20digital%20technologies%2C%20AI%20and%20automation%20are%20some%20more%20areas%20which%20are%20set%20for%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20incorporation%2C%20organisations%20can%20direct%20change%20in%20the%20context%20of%20technology-driven%20and%20automated%20systems.%20These%20approaches%20lead%20towards%20a%20key%20area%20of%20restructuring%20and%20creating%20a%20new%20framework%20for%20the%20future%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20these%20shifts%20are%20redefining%20work%20culture%20and%20signal%20the%20need%20for%20collaborative%2C%20often%20technology-driven%20practices%20while%20also%20nourishing%20interpersonal%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20the%20first%20question%20about%20what%20gives%20this%20new%20form%20of%20work%20its%20meaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20for%20employers%20to%20align%20employees%E2%80%99%20work%20with%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20larger%20purpose%2C%20redesign%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhdl.handle.net%2F10603%2F426859%5C%22%3Eemployee%20retention%20strategies%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eincrease%20their%20sense%20of%20ownership%2C%20enhance%20their%20well-being%20and%20create%20a%20sense%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhdl.handle.net%2F10603%2F426859%5C%22%3Eof%20belonging%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20when%20this%20happens%20that%20employees%20can%20value%20and%20appraise%20their%20jobs%20beyond%20monetary%20terms%20and%20as%20meaningful%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDr.%20Shiwangi%20Sharma%20is%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20S