nd%20if%20Gebbia%20doesn't%20sound%20familiar%2C%20you'll%20surely%20recognize%20the%20other%20company%20he%20cofounded%3A%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20its%20cofounder%2C%20Samara%20has%20roots%20in%20the%20home%20rental%20giant%2C%20having%20previously%20functioned%20as%20its%20in-house%20think%20tank%20and%20design%20studio%20for%20six%20years.%20(Samara%20is%20backed%20by%20Airbnb%20and%20its%20other%20cofounder%2C%20Brian%20Chesky.)%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20which%20became%20its%20own%20entity%20in%202022%20%E2%80%94%20isn't%20in%20the%20business%20of%20renting%20homes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuite%20the%20opposite%3A%20It's%20manufacturing%20factory-built%20accessory%20dwelling%20units%20(ADUs)%2C%20or%20tiny%20homes%2C%20that%20can%20be%20dropped%20into%20Californians'%20backyards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThese%20days%2C%20Samara%20looks%20less%20like%20an%20arm%20of%20Airbnb%20and%20more%20like%20a%20fully%20grounded%20startup.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samara's%20founders%20Joe%20Gebbia%20(left)%20and%20Mike%20McNamara%20(right)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24eb190413ab8e1d892c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamara's%20founders%20Joe%20Gebbia%20(left)%20and%20Mike%20McNamara%20(right)%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20started%20with%20a%20studio%20and%20one-bedroom%20unit%2C%20exclusive%20to%20buyers%20in%20California.%20In%20the%20spring%20of%202023%2C%20it%20expanded%20with%20a%20not-so-tiny%20two-bedroom%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20two-bed%20is%20currently%20Samara%E2%80%99s%20largest%20and%20most%20expensive%20product%2C%20starting%20at%20%24324%2C000%2C%20including%20delivery%20and%20installation.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two-bedroom%20unit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24f2190413ab8e1d8932b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamara%20unveiled%20the%20two-bedroom%20unit%2C%20shown%20in%20a%20rendering%2C%20in%20May%202023.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20bedrooms%20are%20located%20on%20either%20end%20of%20the%2047-foot-long%20unit%2C%20separated%20by%20a%20bathroom%20and%20joint%20living%20room%20and%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20California%20home%20without%20a%20deck.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20bedroom%20rendering%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e253d1ce7f1785b2e5ac03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20two-bed%20unit%2C%20seen%20in%20a%20rendering%2C%20is%2015%20feet%20deep.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20thing%20the%20690-square-foot%20unit%20has%20two%20%E2%80%94%20one%20with%20glass%20double%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENot%20big%20enough%3F%20A%20two-bedroom%2C%20two-bathroom%20option%20will%20be%20ready%20in%20April.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22workers%20in%20factory%20building%20tiny%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24fb3ce7f1785b2e5a8fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamara's%20new%20manufacturing%20facility%20is%20located%20in%20Mexico%2C%20about%20five%20miles%20south%20of%20the%20border.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20addition%2C%20Mike%20McNamara%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Samara%2C%20says%20the%20company%20will%20have%20a%20complete%20product%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDespite%20their%20heftier%20costs%20and%20sizes%2C%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20CEO%20believes%20its%20largest%20units%20will%20also%20be%20its%20most%20popular.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two-bedroom%20interior%20rendering%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24fda90413ab8e1d893d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20two-bedroom%20option%2C%20shown%20in%20a%20rendering%2C%20looks%20like%20any%20single-family%20home.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20give%20up%20your%20backyard%2C%20you%20might%20as%20well%20get%20as%20much%20money%20out%20of%20it%20as%20possible%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20rent%20on%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0especially%20one%20with%20two%20bathrooms%20%E2%80%94%20will%20always%20be%20higher%20than%20a%20one-bed%20or%20studio.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EADUs%20have%20varying%20uses%2C%20from%20home%20offices%20to%20guest%20residences.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22desk%20next%20to%20a%20plant%2C%20rendering%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e2503190413ab8e1d893f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBackyard%20ADUs%2C%20shown%20in%20a%20rendering%2C%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20source%20of%20passive%20income.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20McNamara%20says%20about%2040%25%20of%20its%20customers%20will%20likely%20use%20it%20as%20a%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20put%20one%20of%20these%20things%20in%20your%20backyard%2C%20and%20in%20most%20cases%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20you'll%20make%20money%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Northern%20California%2C%20which%20flexes%20higher%20rent%20than%20Southern%20California%2C%20is%20Samara's%20bread%20and%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENo%2C%20its%20customers%20aren%E2%80%99t%20exclusively%20Silicon%20Valley%20tech%20bros.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22samara's%20studio%20apartment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e25044ce7f1785b2e5a9aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENorthern%20California%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Battractive%20market%26quot%3B%20for%20Samara%2C%20its%20CEO%20said.%20A%20rendering%20of%20its%20studio%20is%20shown%20above.%20%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20buyers%20all%20have%20one%20thing%20in%20common%3A%20equity%2C%20either%20from%20their%20employers'%20stock%20options%20or%20home%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20multi-generational%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20McNamara%20said%2C%20citing%20an%20example%20of%20a%20customer%20who%20has%20held%20onto%20their%20Bay%20Area%20home%20for%20decades%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Btremendous%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20accumulated%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20modular%2C%20factory-built%20home%20without%20a%20manufacturing%20facility.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22modular%20home%20in%20a%20factory%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24d01ce7f1785b2e5a685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnlike%20traditional%20construction%20sites%2C%20Samara%20won't%20have%20to%20plan%20its%20projects%20around%20poor%20weather%20conditions.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20mass-manufactured%20product%2C%20modular%20construction%20outshines%20traditional%20homebuilding%20methods%20in%20two%20areas%3A%20efficiency%20and%20cost%20predictability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamara%20has%20already%20delivered%20several%20units%2C%20according%20to%20its%20CEO.%20But%20those%20were%20of%20previous%20models%2C%20built%20using%20an%20outsourced%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20startup%20announced%20it%20had%20acquired%20its%20own%20150%2C000-square-foot%20factory%20in%20Mexico%2C%20about%20five%20miles%20south%20of%20the%20US%20border.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22picture%20of%20a%20factory%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e250c96080194819fbe8be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamara's%20factory%20is%20located%20in%20Mexicali%2C%20Mexico.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20acquisition%20was%20Samara's%20final%20puzzle%20piece%20to%20bring%20everything%20in-house%2C%20from%20design%20to%20engineering%20to%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20McNamara%2C%20it's%20what%20sets%20the%20company%20apart%20from%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-starter-homes-manufactured-modular-housing-failing-real-estate-construction-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodular%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20have%20been%20crumbling%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20contractor%20outsourcing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EArmed%20with%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%2C%20the%20startup%20says%20it%20can%20now%20cut%20delivery%20times%20while%20increasing%20quality%20control.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tiny%20home%20inside%20a%20factory%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24d2290413ab8e1d89198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcNamara%20said%20the%20factory's%20first%20unit%20will%20be%20shipped%20out%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%20%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20factory%20is%20in%20full%20swing%2C%20the%20company's%20CEO%20said%20it'll%20be%20able%20to%20churn%20out%20a%20delivery-ready%20ADU%20in%20one%20month%20and%201%2C000%20in%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20expect%20Amazon%20Prime-level%20delivery%20times.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20rendering%20of%20a%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e250fc90413ab8e1d894a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20model%20has%20a%20kitchen%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20a%20rendering.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESamara%20handles%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20construction%2C%20delivery%2C%20and%20installation%20process.%20Less%20exciting%20factors%2C%20like%20permitting%20and%20soil%20surveys%2C%20extend%20its%20lead%20time%20to%20seven%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20home%20can%20be%20delivered%2C%20the%20team%20must%20also%20spend%20about%20six%20weeks%20on%20its%20customer's%20property%2C%20laying%20the%20tiny%20home's%20foundation%20and%20establishing%20on-site%20utility%20hookups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20the%20ADU%2C%20foundation%2C%20and%20permits%20are%20finally%20complete%2C%20a%20truck%20will%20deliver%20the%20product%20to%20the%20customer's%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22backyard%20tiny%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e24de9ce7f1785b2e5a72e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20takes%20about%2020%20minutes%20for%20the%20home%20to%20be%20craned%20onto%20its%20foundation%2C%20Samara's%20CEO%20said.%3Cp%3ESamara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20the%20fun%20begins%2C%20or%20as%20McNamara%20said%2C%20when%20the%20home%20%26quot%3Bflies%20through%20the%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20on-site%2C%20a%20crane%20will%20drop%20the%20home%20onto%20its%20foundation.%20After%20it's%20bolted%20into%20place%20and%20cleaned%2C%20it'll%20be%20Airbnb-ready%20within%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERegulations%2C%20such%20as%20bu