.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20landscape%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20changed%20soon%20after%20Mr%20Scindia's%20defeat%20as%20a%20coup%20led%20by%20him%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%2015-month-old%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Scindia%20-%20once%20close%20to%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20-%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20March%202020%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20Delhi%20and%20shortly%20after%20his%20exit%2C%2021%20Congress%20MLAs%20loyal%20to%20him%20also%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20switch%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20co-founded%20by%20his%20grandmother%20Vijaya%20Raje%20Scindia%2C%20soon%20after%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20a%20berth%20in%20the%20Union%20Cabinet.%20His%20two%20aunts%20-%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20and%20Yashodhara%20Raje%20-%20are%20also%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20much-anticipated%20announcement%2C%20the%20BJP%20this%20evening%20released%20the%20first%20list%20of%20195%20candidates.%20The%20list%20includes%20PM%20Modi%20from%20his%20constituency%20Varanasi%20and%2034%20ministers%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20finalised%2024%20names%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20was%20replaced%20by%20the%20party%20leadership%20as%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20Mohan%20Yadav%20after%20assembly%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Vidisha%20constituency.%20This%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20win%20for%20Mr%20Chouhan%20who%2C%20sources%20say%2C%20was%20offered%20the%20Bhopal%20seat%20which%20he%20rejected%20and%20conveyed%20his%20desire%20to%20fight%20from%20Vidisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20BJP's%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20(CEC)%20met%20on%20Thursday%20night%20to%20deliberate%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20(NDA)%20won%20a%20total%20of%20303%20seats%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20behind%20at%2052%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709390580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F26i4t0u_jyotiraditya-scindia-amit-shah-ani_625x300_02_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-union-minister-jyotiraditya-scindia-named-for-lok-sabha-seat-he-lost-to-bjp-in-2019-polls-5163739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Aviation%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20will%20be%20contesting%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Guna%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20seat%20he%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-union-minister-jyotiraditya-scindia-named-for-lok-sabha-seat-he-lost-to-bjp-in-2019-polls-5163739%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-union-minister-jyotiraditya-scindia-named-for-lok-sabha-seat-he-lost-to-bjp-in-2019-polls-5163739%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-union-minister-jyotiraditya-scindia-named-for-lok-sabha-seat-he-lost-to-bjp-in-2019-polls-5163739%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ohio%20woman%20believes%20her%20Stanley%20cup%20took%20a%20bullet%20for%20her%2C%20says%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22923%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Stanley%2040oz%20straw%20Quencher.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65958cbcec62ab5daf804eb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Stanley%2040oz%20straw%20Quenc