%20to%20speak%20to%20him.%20All%20this%20while%20he%20has%20played%20Ranji%20and%20then%20played%20white-ball%20cricket.%20Has%20it%20made%20him%20a%20poorer%20player%3F%20It%20hasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20players%20picked%20in%20Delhi%20Capitals%20have%20played%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy%2C%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20and%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20Even%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishant%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F900-ishant-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshant%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20played%20Ranji.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Khaleel%20Ahmed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107233-khaleel-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKhaleel%20Ahmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20played%20the%20full%20season%20after%20a%20long%20time.%20We%20worked%20with%20him%20in%20the%20off%20season%20and%20got%20him%20fit%20to%20play%20Ranji.%C2%A0There%20are%20only%20one%20or%20two%20exceptions%20who%20need%20to%20be%20spoken%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20that%20with%20the%20dropping%20of%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20central%20contracts%2C%20whether%20the%20ficus%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20relevance%20of%20first-class%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20someone%20has%20not%20played%20or%20ignored%20red-ball%20domestic%20cricket.%20Otherwise%2C%20all%20of%20them%20have%20played%20Ranji%20Trophy%20when%20they%20were%20free.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20BCCI%20will%20take%20proper%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Shah%20has%20earlier%20mentioned%20Ishan%20Kishan%20during%20an%20interaction%20but%20quickly%20added%20that%20the%20announcement%20was%20not%20targeted%20t