e's%20got%20to%20number%20one%20in%20the%20world.%20He's%20a%20world-class%20bowler%20and%20from%20our%20point%20of%20view%20we%20weren't%20surprised%20that%20he%20put%20up%20a%20performance%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2041%2C%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0continues%20to%20lead%20the%20England%20attack.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Zaheer%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F257-zaheer-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EZaheer%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20someone%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20a%20lot%20to%20try%20and%20learn%20from.%20How%20he%20used%20the%20reverse%20swing%2C%20how%20he%20covered%20the%20ball%20when%20he%20ran%20into%20bowl%2C%20that's%20something%20I%20tried%20to%20sort%20of%20develop%20on%20the%20back%20of%20playing%20against%20him%20quite%20a%20few%20times%20here%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0told%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaheer%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20finest%20seamers%2C%20played%20his%20last%20Test%20in%202014%20when%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20his%20game.%20Among%20the%20current%20lot%20of%20Indian%20pacers%2C%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0is%20most%20impressed%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E's%20ability%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20exponent%26quot%3B%20of%20reverse%20swing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709388720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F70vft8do_james-anderson-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_24_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fits-a-shame-james-andersons-blockbuster-comment-on-india-stars-absence-in-test-series-5163610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22James%20Anderson%20is%20just%20two%20more%20scalps%20away%20from%20700%20Test%20wickets%20as%20he%20prepares%20himself%20for%20the%20fifth%20Test%20of%20the%20ongoing%20five-match%20Test%20series%20against%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%20%7C%20Note%20How%20the%20Machiavellian%20Media%20Cheers%20Loudly%20as%20Elections%20Are%20Stolen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05113839%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%E2%80%99s%20affection%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20a%20many-layered%20thing%20%E2%80%93%20and%20certainly%20one%20of%20the%20layers%20is%20the%20financial%20reward%20that%20flows%20seamlessly%20to%20the%20proprietors%20of%20media%20houses.%20But%20must%20this%20amorous%20relationship%20extend%20to%20unqualified%20support%20for%20the%20perfidy%20that%20has%20become%20the%20hallmark%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20drive%20to%20wrest%20for%20itself%20everlasting%20and%20uninterrupted%20political%20power%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverturning%20the%20popular%20vote%20through%20money-fuelled%2C%20behind-the-scenes%2C%20machinations%20must%20surely%20be%20considered%20nothing%20less%20than%20running%20a%20bulldozer%20through%20the%20three%20pillars%20of%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20even%20for%20incorrigible%20crawlers%3F%20Match%20fixing%20in%20cricket%20has%20been%20severely%20condemned%20by%20the%20media%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20so%20why%20is%20this%20permanent%20forbearance%20extended%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20steal%2C%20snatch%2C%20stitch%20together%20electoral%20victories%20based%20on%20a%20foundation%20of%20bribery%2C%20lies%20and%20sleight%20of%20hand%3F%20Is%20this%20unadulterated%20media%20glee%2C%20for%20what%20has%20been%20euphemistically%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Lotus%E2%80%99%20(Operation%20Loot-Us%20would%20perhaps%20have%20been%20a%20more%20apt%20moniker)%2C%20actually%20encouraging%20more%20predatory%20expeditions%20of%20this%20kind%3F%20What%20is%20the%20cumulative%20impact%20of%20such%20undisguised%20media%20admiration%20for%20stealing%20elections%20on%20political%20and%20public%20morality%20in%20this%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20all%20the%20world%20loves%20a%20winner.%20Mediapersons%20know%20their%20Chanakya%20and%20their%20Machiavelli%20well%2C%20they%20understand%20the%20wisdom%20that%20political%20parties%20should%20never%20attempt%20to%20win%20by%20force%20what%20can%20be%20won%20by%20deception.%20They%20cannot%20but%20be%20persuaded%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Jaiveer%20Shergill%2C%20graduate%20in%20law%20from%20a%20swish%20US%20law%20school%20who%20also%20graduated%20from%20being%20a%20Congress%20spokesperson%20to%20a%20BJP%20one%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye.%20He%20recently%20tweeted%3A%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20knows%20how%20to%20win%20a%20losing%20battle%20%26amp%3B%20Congress%20knows%20how%20to%20lose%20a%20winning%20battle!%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20difference%20!!%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0(%3Cem%3EHaha%2C%20Mr%20Shergill%2C%20hope%20you%20get%20rewarded%20for%20your%20wit%20with%20a%20RS%20nomination%20in%20the%20not%20too%20distant%20future!)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20developments%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20demonstrated%20this%20with%20sharp%20clarity%3A%20the%20mayoral%20election%20to%20the%20Chandigarh%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20January%2030%20and%2C%20almost%20a%20month%20later%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20its%20fallout%20in%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mayoral%20poll%20for%20Chandigarh%20could%20not%20have%20been%20more%20clearly%20and%20unequivocally%20fraudulent%20and%20it%20played%20out%20in%20full%20public%20view.%20Although%20the%20media%20were%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20hall%20where%20the%20election%20was%20being%20conducted%2C%20a%20large%20screen%20had%20been%20thoughtfully%20installed%20to%20ensure%20that%20newspersons%20could%20follow%20the%20developments%20live.%20Everybody%20got%20to%20see%20the%20Returning%20Office%20Anil%20Masih%20scribbling%20away%20on%20eight%20ballot%20papers%20that%20had%20gone%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance.%20These%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20later%2C%20were%20defaced%20and%20therefore%20invalid.%20Immediately%20after%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%2C%20Manoj%20Sonkar%2C%20was%20declared%20victorious%2C%20had%20ladoos%20stuffed%20into%20his%20mouth%20and%20before%20long%20was%20eased%20into%20the%20mayoral%20chair%20with%20party%20colleagues%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20Chandigarh%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher%2C%20signaling%20%E2%80%98V%E2%80%99%20for%20victory%20signs%20and%20applauding%20from%20the%20sidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08121514%2FUntitled-design-4-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08121514%2FUntitled-design-4-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08121514%2FUntitled-design-4-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08121514%2FUntitled-design-4-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnil%20Masih%2C%20caught%20on%20CCTV%20camera.%20Photo%3A%20Video%20screengrab%2FX%2F%40sardesairajdeep%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverybody%2C%20including%20mediapersons%2C%20knew%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%2014%20councillors%20in%20the%2035-member%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20while%20AAP-Congress%20coalition%20could%20marshal%2020%20(AAP%2013%20and%20Congress%207).%20Everybody%2C%20including%20mediapersons%2C%20knew%20that%20the%20presiding%20officer%2C%20Masih%2C%20is%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20minority%20cell.%20Yet%2C%20apart%20from%20a%20handful%20of%20newspapers%20which%20raised%20serious%20questions%20on%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20election%20was%20conducted%2C%20most%20from%20the%20media%20preferred%20to%20keep%20their%20eyes%20wide%20shut%20on%20the%20less%20than%20scrupulous%20manner%20in%20which%20Sonkar%20was%20pronounced%20as%20victorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20was%20headlined%3A%20%E2%80%98BJP%20wins%20Chandigarh%20mayor%20poll%20as%208%20INDIA%20votes%20invalidated%E2%80%99.%20The%20report%20alluded%20to%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfraud%2C%20forgery%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csedition%E2%80%9D%20being%20made%2C%20but%20did%20not%20go%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20confirm%20this%20although%20gathering%20such%20evidence%20should%20really%20not%20have%20occasioned%20much%20effort.%20Others%20were%20even%20more%20blatant.%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20TV%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20its%20web%20report%20headlined%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%20mayoral%20polls%3A%20BJP%20candidate%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20wins%20post%20of%20mayor%2C%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20fails%E2%80%99%2C%20did%20not%20even%20bother%20to%20mention%20the%20invalidated%20ballots.%20%3Cem%3EZee%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20avoid%20mentioning%20the%20allegations%20but%20nevertheless%20bravely%20shouted%20out%20loud%20and%20clear%20that%20%E2%80%98BJP%20Dominates%20Chandigarh%20Mayor%20Election%20with%2016%20Votes%E2%80%99.%20%3Cem%3EAAJ%20Tak%3C%2Fem%3E%20crowed%3A%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%20Mayor%20Chunav%3A%2013%20Plus%207%20Minus%208%E2%80%A6Aur%20Jeet%20Gayi%20BJP%2C%20Aise%20Bhigad%20Gaya%20Congress-AAP%20ka%20Game%E2%80%99.%20Its%20coverage%20was%20full%20of%20%E2%80%9Canalyses%E2%80%9D%20on%20how%20the%20BJP%20had%20swung%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20effort%20of%20scribes%20and%20anchors%20was%20to%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20to%20higlight%20the%20ineffectuality%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%20TV%3C%2Fem%3E%20predictably%20went%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20pour%20scorn%20on%20every%20claim%20that%20the%20poll%20was%20rigged.%20Its%20headline%20said%20it%20all%3A%20%E2%80%98Defeated%20Indi%20Accuses%20BJP%20of%20%E2%80%9CCheating%E2%80%9D%20In%20Chandigarh%E2%80%99.%20Its%20prime%20time%20exposition%20bowled%20several%20googlies%20at%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc%3A%20%E2%80%98Can%20Indi%20bounce%20back%20from%20this%20debacle%3F%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Indi%20Fails%20Litmus%20Test%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Indi%E2%80%99s%20local%20failure%20to%20hit%202024%20Goals%3F%E2%80%99%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20publications%20ventured%20to%20question%20the%20blatant%20subversion%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%20There%20was%2C%20fortunately%2C%20the%20odd%20one%20like%20%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20in%20its%20January%2031%20report%20pulled%20no%20punches%3A%20%E2%80%98Democracy%20on%20edge%20as%20BJP%20steals%20Chandigarh%20election%20from%20Congress-AAP%20alliance%E2%80%99.%20It%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20perverted%20election%20process%20raised%20concerns%20about%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20the%20coming%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20a%20near%20repeat%20of%20this%20scenario%20during%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20manoeuvres%20to%20engineer%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%2C%20rather%20ungrammatically%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccross%20voting%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20%C2%A0(one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20vote%2C%20one%20%E2%80%9Ccross-votes%E2%80%9D!).%20Consider%20again%20how%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20applauded%20the%20goings-on%20through%20the%20use%20of%20selective%20information%20and%20curated%20words.%20Its%20February%2028%20headline%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20snatches%20RS%20wins%20in%20UP%2C%20HP%3B%20Himachal%20CM%20in%20trouble%E2%80%9D.%20Words%20like%20%E2%80%9Csnatch%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cstunned%E2%80%9D%2C%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20report%2C%20reflecting%20a%20little%20concealed%20glee%20over%20the%20developments%2C%20along%20with%20expressions%20like%20%E2%80%9Csmug%20ineptness%20of%20rivals%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cpushing%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20govt%20in%20Himachal%20into%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20life-threatening%20crisis%20three%20days%20before%20the%20state%20budget%20is%20to%20be%20presented%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20a%20naked%20display%20of%20money%20power%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20the%20full%20muscle%20of%20the%20central%20government%20at%20play%2C%20was%20framed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cambushes%E2%80%9D%20that%20dealt%20%E2%80%9Canother%20psychological%20blow%20to%20the%20opposition%E2%80%9D.%20Striking%2C%20too%2C%20was%20the%20way%20the%20same%20newspaper%20was%20quick%20to%20fault%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Cweakening%20oversight%20of%20states%E2%80%9D%20but%20had%20not%20a%20word%20on%20what%20seemed%20highly%20dubious%20means%20employed%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20gain%20the%20Himachal%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20the%20Congress%20was%20simply%20imploding%20of%20its%20own%20volition%20with%20no%20external%20factors%20creating%20the%20conditions%20necessary%20for%20such%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimplosion%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelevision%20news%20is%20absolutely%20blatant%20in%20its%20genuflection%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20prime%20minister.%20The%20trouble%20the%20print%20correspondents%20of%20Big%20Media%20is%20that%20they%20would%20like%20to%20appear%20as%20independent-minded%2C%20thinking%2C%20analytical%20women%20and%20men%2C%20but%20scratch%20them%20and%20they%20are%20all%20shown%20to%20be%20equally%20deferential%20to%20the%20power%20brokers%20setting%20the%20news%20agenda!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20needed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20firmly%20call%20out%20charades%20like%20these.%20In%20its%20verdict%20of%20February%2020%20on%20the%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20fraud%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20of%20the%20considered%20view%20that%20in%20such%20a%20case%2C%20this%20Court%20is%20duty-bound%E2%80%A6to%20do%20complete%20justice%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20process%20of%20electoral%20democracy%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20be%20thwarted%20by%20such%20subterfuges.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestion%20is%2C%20are%20not%20the%20media%20similarly%20duty-bound%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%20anniversary%20of%20the%20IT%20Rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20have%20passed%20since%20then%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%2C%20along%20with%20the%20then%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Prakash%20Javadekar%2C%20dropped%20their%20bombshell%20that%20went%20by%20the%20nomenclature%20%E2%80%98Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%E2%80%99.%20Remember%20how%20Prasad%20bombastically%20began%20that%20news%20conference%3F%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20welcomes%20criticism%20and%20the%20right%20to%20dissent%20but%20let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%E2%80%A6%20social%20media%20users%20running%20into%20crores%20should%20also%20be%20given%20a%20proper%20forum%20for%20the%20resolution%20of%20their%20grievances%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20being%20fair%20to%20social%20media%20users%20that%20this%20step%20%E2%80%93%20sold%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20touch%20oversight%20mechanism%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20was%20launched.%20Yet%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20what%20became%20more%20and%20more%20obvious%20was%20that%20the%20entity%20that%20gained%20the%20greatest%20heft%20from%20these%20rules%20was%20of%20course%20the%20Modi%20government%20itself.%20Guidelines%2C%20notifications%20and%20orders%20flowed%20seamlessly%20from%20the%20top%20to%20make%20the%20Rules%20more%20rigorous.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20those%20who%20got%20to%20decide%20on%20how%20%E2%80%9Cgrievances%E2%80%9D%20of%20social%20media%20users%20were%20to%20be%20redressed%20are%20in%20lockstep%20with%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20have%20taken%20their%20eyes%20off%20this%20story%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20take%20a%20quick%20look%20at%20the%20various%20additions%2Falterations%20made%20to%20the%20original%20rules.%20In%202022%2C%20intermediaries%20were%20required%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20users%20did%20not%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%2C%20upload%20or%20share%20prohibited%20content%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20other%20words%20they%20were%20to%20function%20as%20first%20responder-censor.%20In%202023%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20regulating%20online%20gaming%2C%20the%20PIB%20was%20brought%20into%20the%20picture.%20Anything%20that%20the%20PIB%20considers%20fake%20now%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20down%20to%20avoid%20liability.%20This%20was%20seen%20as%20problematic%20because%20a%20state%20agency%20now%20had%20the%20power%20to%20decide%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%20down%20and%20what%20retained.%20That%20year%2C%20the%20emergency%20powers%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%20were%20used%20to%20block%20the%20BBC%20documentary%20series%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Modi%20Question%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20IT%20Rules%20were%20once%20again%20amended%20%E2%80%93%20a%20change%20that%20is%20interesting%20to%20say%20the%20least%20in%20this%20pre-election%20era%3A%20Now%20not%20just%20the%20%E2%80%98security%20agency%E2%80%99%2C%20even%20bureaucrats%20like%20the%20home%20secretary%20can%20order%2C%20every%20six%20month%2C%20the%20destruction%20of%20records%20of%20government%20interceptions%20and%C2%A0%20its%20attempts%20to%20decrypt%20encrypted%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20shortly%20after%20Messrs%20Shankar%20and%20Javdekar%20gifted%20us%20with%20these%20IT%20Rules%2C%20Digipub%2C%20a%20platform%20representing%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20online%20media%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20Rules%20appear%20to%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cgo%20against%20the%20fundamental%20principle%20of%20news%20and%20its%20role%20in%20a%20democracy%E2%80%9D%20in%20some%20places.%20%C2%A0It%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20draw%20your%20attention%20to%20the%20well%20settled%20jurisprudence%20on%20news%20media.%20A%20publication%20relating%20to%20current%20affairs%20represents%20not%20only%20the%20author%20or%20publisher%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20right%20to%20expression%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20but%20also%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20be%20informed%20and%20to%20have%20access%20to%20differing%20viewpoints.%20For%20the%20executive%20to%20have%20the%20absolute%20power%20to%20regulate%20the%20content%20of%20news%20portals%20or%20publications%20would%20be%20to%20strike%20not%20only%20at%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20but%20at%20democracy%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20alerted%20the%20government%20to%20some%20anomalies%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Rules%20as%20drafted%2C%20expression%20may%20invite%20adverse%20consequential%20action%2C%20such%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20defamation.%20Such%20action%20should%20only%20happen%20after%20adjudication%20by%20open%20courts%20of%20law%2C%20on%20legal%20principles.%20This%20entire%20legal%20process%20is%20bypassed%20by%20the%20Rules%2C%20in%20as%20much%20as%2C%20upon%20a%20complaint%20of%20defamation%2C%20a%20body%20consisting%20of%20bureaucrats%20and%20controlled%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%20may%20decide%20the%20merits%20and%20block%20access%20to%20the%20content%20of%20any%20current%20affairs%20publication.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20years%20since%20these%20observations%20have%20only%20provided%20evidence%20after%20evidence%20of%20the%20accuracy%20of%20Digipub%E2%80%99s%20cautionary%20notes.%20The%20IT%20Rules%20have%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20schema%20that%20gives%20and%20gives%20the%20Central%20Government%20the%20freedom%20to%20take%20and%20take%20away%20our%20freedoms%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENBDSA%E2%80%99s%20slap%20on%20the%20wrist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20chastisement%20and%20fines%20imposed%20by%20the%20News%20Broadcasting%20and%20Digital%20Standards%20Authority%20(NBDSA)%20on%20television%20news%20shows%20that%20communalised%20news%20events%20like%20the%20Shradda%20Walker%20case%20and%20the%20Ram%20Navami%20violence%2C%20were%20perceived%20as%20too%20little%20slight%20a%20measure%20which%20came%20far%20too%20late.%20%C2%A0They%20barely%20addressed%20the%20extent%20of%20social%20harm%20the%20programmes%20perpetrated.%20As%20one%20tweet%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CAny%20point%20imposing%20such%20meagre%20penalties%20when%20they%20make%20crores%20selling%20h%40te%3F%20If%20the%20NBDSA%20is%20serious%20about%20tackling%20this%2C%20the%20anchors%20should%20be%20ordered%20to%20apologise%20on%20air.%E2%80%9D%20Other%20suggestions%20for%20more%20effective%20censure%20were%20also%20proffered%2C%20including%20taking%20these%20programmes%20off%20the%20air%20for%20a%20week%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20merit%20in%20these%20observations.%20The%20argument%20that%20the%20punishment%20meted%20out%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20symbolic%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20cut%20much%20ice%20in%20an%20age%20when%20communal%20hatreds%20are%20manufactured%20on%20an%20industrial%20scale.%20It%20is%20only%20when%20the%20business%20model%20of%20hate%20generation%20fails%20conclusively%20will%20proprietors%20of%20these%20media%20houses%20really%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20the%20required%20action.%20Until%20then%20they%20will%20carry%20on%20hiring%20such%20anchors%20precisely%20because%20their%20brand%20of%20journalism%20represents%20a%20winning%20formula%20that%20bring%20in%20eyeballs%20and%20the%20advertising%20rupee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20other%20big%20question%3A%20why%20were%20so%20many%20other%20worthy%20contenders%20for%20public%20shaming%20left%20out%3F%20The%20anchor%20of%20%3Cem%3ESundarshan%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Suresh%20Chavhanke%2C%20of%20%E2%80%98UPSC%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20fame%2C%20had%20even%20participated%20in%20a%20public%20programme%20that%20called%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20Muslims.%20Truly%20it%20is%20time%20this%20lot%20is%20defunded%2C%20both%20socially%20and%20financially%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20is%20the%20NBDSA%3F%20While%20print%20media%20had%20its%20traditional%20regulators%20like%20the%20Press%20Council%2C%20private%20television%20which%20came%20into%20their%20own%20only%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20resisted%20external%20regulation%20and%20opted%20for%20what%20was%20framed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cself%20regulation%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20a%20group%20of%20private%20news%20broadcasters%20set%20up%20the%20NBDSA%20to%20deal%20with%20ethical%20issues%20that%20may%20arise%20in%20terms%20of%20television%20news%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApex%20court%E2%80%99s%20two-handed%20verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELong%20time%20Wire%20reader%2C%20Sumanta%20Banerjee%20writes%20in%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CApropos%20%E2%80%98Moral%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Story%3A%20Information%20Is%20Essential%20for%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20(February%2017)%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dragged%20its%20feet%20for%20seven%20long%C2%A0years%C2%A0to%C2%A0come%C2%A0to%C2%A0a%C2%A0judgment%C2%A0on%C2%A0the%C2%A0issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20after%20declaring%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20as%20illegal%2C%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20ordered%20the%20freezing%20of%20the%20cash%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20other%20parties%20have%20accumulated%20through%20the%20scheme%20and%20still%20holds%20on%20to.%20There%20is%20thus%20a%20loophole%20left%20in%20the%20judgment%20that%20will%20be%20utilised%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20which%20can%20continue%20to%20spend%20that%20illegally%20acquired%20money%20on%20their%20campaigns%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20%3Cem%3Ereal%20moral%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20the%20story%20is%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20apex%20court%20with%20one%20hand%20delivers%20a%20verdict%20that%20upholds%20constitutional%20norms%2C%20while%20with%20the%20other%20hand%20behind%20its%20back%2C%20allows%20vested%20interests%20to%20retain%20their%20ill-gotten%20wealth%20by%20refusing%20to%20penalise%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFardeen%20alias%20Swami%20Aatm%20Gaurav%20writes%20to%20Arfa%20Khanum%20Sherwani%2C%20senior%20editor%20at%20the%20Wire%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EI%20have%20been%20following%20your%20telecasts%20on%20various%20issues.%20Out%20of%20millions%20of%20Muslims%20alive%20on%20the%20planet%20today%2C%20I%20am%20one%20of%20the%20non-conventional%20few.%20I%20am%20basically%20an%20Osho%20disciple.%20It%20is%20a%20well%20known%20fact%20that%20Osho%20was%20against%20the%20concept%20of%20religions.%20He%20stood%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%98religiousness%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20present%20tumultuous%20times%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20also%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20we%20need%20a%20very%20special%20vision%20and%20I%20believe%20Osho%20is%20one%20person%20who%20holds%20the%20key%20to%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20in%20India%20is%20grim.%20Anyone%20who%20believes%20in%20humanity%20needs%20to%20raise%20their%20voice%20against%20this%20present%20regime.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20context%2C%20I%20need%20to%20say%20one%20thing.%20Muslims%20of%20India%20have%20not%20been%20thankful%20enough%20for%20what%20they%20got%20in%20this%20country%E2%80%A6It%20is%20time%20that%20they%20wholeheartedly%20accept%20their%20sense%20of%20belonging%20to%20this%20country%E2%80%A6Let%20Muslims%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20declare%20that%20they%20are%20Sufis%20now%20and%20not%20identified%20with%20petty%20propagandising%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Islam.%20The%20only%20way%20this%20regime%20can%20be%20punished%20is%20by%20Muslims%20exhibiting%20their%20elevated%20selves!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWrite%20to%20%3Cem%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709387957000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05113839%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-note-how-the-machiavellian-media-cheers-loudly-as-elections-are-stolen%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-note-how-the-machiavellian-media-cheers-loudly-as-elections-are-stolen%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Textile%20unit%20invests%20Rs%20120%20crore%20in%20Kathua%2C%20to%20employ%20650%20youths%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709387861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-08%2F09%2Ffull%2F1660069007-1418.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftextile-unit-invests-rs-120-crore-in-kathua-to-employ-650-youths-124030200627_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bloomtex%20Industries%20is%20one%20of%20the%20industrial%20units%20that%20has%20set%20up%20their%20unit%20in%20SIDCO%2C%20the%20new%20industrial%20estate%20at%20Kathua's%20Bhagthali%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3