%80%9Cact%20urgently%E2%80%9D%20to%20review%20whether%20Israel%20was%20complying%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhuman-rights%2Ft-17455099%5C%22%3Ehuman%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20standards%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEric%20Mamer%2C%20a%20speaker%20for%20the%20European%20Commission%20in%20Brussels%2C%20said%20his%20office%20was%20looking%20into%20the%20request.%20The%20European%20Commission%20declined%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20incident%20where%20over%20100%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20on%20Thursday%20as%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20reach%20an%20aid%20convoy.%20Gazan%20health%20officials%20reported%20scores%20of%20victims%20delivered%20to%20hospitals%20with%20gunshot%20wounds.%20Israeli%20officials%20said%20most%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVon%20der%20Leyen%20has%20called%20for%20an%20independent%20international%20investigation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20determine%20what%20has%20happened%2C%20we%20are%20not%20attributing%20blame%20or%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20speaker%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20find%20out%20was%20has%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Feu-to-release-vital-funds-for-palestinian-aid-organization-unrwa%2Fa-68423061%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20translated%20from%20German%2C%20and%20was%20first%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709378998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131712%2F2620419248_a4fa7326fc_o-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fafter-suspending-aid-money-over-israeli-allegations-eu-to-resume-payments-to-palestines-unrwa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20European%20Union%20had%20suspended%20relief%20money%20to%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20for%20a%20month%20after%20Israel%20accused%20the%