ire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F02122914%2FUntitled-design-22.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20rare%20case%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20given%20the%20international%20tag%20to%20the%20sensitive%20defence%20airport%20at%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Jamnagar%20town%20for%20just%2010%20days%20so%20that%20guests%20invited%20to%20the%20wedding%20of%20Mukesh%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20son%20can%20land%20close%20to%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20tag%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20airport%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20border%20was%20given%20for%20February%2025%20to%20March%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20businessman%20Ambani%2C%20a%20fellow%20Gujarati%20seen%20close%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20is%20hosting%20many%20guests%20from%20the%20global%20who%E2%80%99s%20who%20list%20arriving%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20to%20attend%20son%20Anant%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20wedding%20to%20Radhika%20Merchant%2C%20daughter%20of%20industrialist%20Viren%20Merchant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20airport%20officials%2C%20between%20February%2028%20and%20March%204%2C%20the%20Jamnagar%20airport%20is%20expected%20to%20receive%20at%20least%20150%20aircraft.%20%E2%80%9COf%20these%2C%2050%20are%20flying%20in%20directly%20from%20foreign%20locations.%20During%20these%20five%20days%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20than%20300%20aircraft%20movements%20at%20the%20airport%2C%E2%80%9D%20D.K.%20Singh%2C%20airport%20director%20at%20Jamnagar%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20said%20approximately%202%2C000%20guests%20are%20expected%20at%20the%20pre-wedding%20event%20in%20these%20aircraft%2C%20including%20guests%20from%20Mumbai%20and%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20multi-fold%20jump%20in%20aircraft%20movements%20for%20the%20Jamnagar%20airport%2C%20which%2C%20on%20average%2C%20handles%20only%20three%20scheduled%20and%20five%20non-scheduled%20aircraft%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fvariety%2Fjamnagars-skies-jam-packed-with-sleek-jets-ferrying-ambani-guests%2Farticle67895288.ece%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fjamnagar-airport-gets-international-status-for-anant-ambanis-pre-wedding-bash%2Farticle67904245.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20have%20pressed%20in%20resources%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Custom%2C%20Immigration%20and%20Quarantine%20(CIQ)%20facility%20at%20the%20airport.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEspecially%20for%20the%20wedding%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20has%20not%20only%20permitted%20access%20of%20these%20private%20aircraft%20to%20its%20sensitive%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%E2%80%9D%20area%2C%20also%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20preparation%20for%20the%20massive%20inflow%20of%20guests%2C%20the%20AAI%20(Airports%20Authority%20of%20India)%20has%20expanded%20the%20size%20of%20its%20passenger%20building%20from%20475%20sq%20km%20to%20900%20sq%20m%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20accommodate%20nearly%20360%20passengers%20during%20peak%20hours%20as%20compared%20to%20180%20earlier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20airport%20official%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CExpansion%20work%20was%20planned%20much%20earlier%20but%20was%20expedited%20for%20the%20(Ambani%20wedding)%20event.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%E2%80%9Cup%20to%20three%20aircraft%20are%20being%20accommodated%20in%20the%20technical%20area%20at%20a%20given%20time%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20news%20report%20highlighted%20that%20the%20airport%20has%20also%20enhanced%20manpower%20in%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20vertical%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThirty-five%20house-keeping%20staff%20have%20been%20added%20to%20the%20existing%20strength%20of%2016%3B%20the%20(BJP-ruled)%20state%20(Gujarat)%20government%20has%20also%20doubled%20the%20deployment%20of%20security%20personnel%20from%2035%20to%2070%3B%20ground%20handling%20agencies%20have%20raised%20the%20strength%20of%20their%20staff%20from%2065%20to%20125%2C%E2%80%9D%20underlined%20%C2%A0The%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbani%E2%80%99s%20Reliance%20Industries%20has%20also%20been%20allowed%20to%20make%20special%20arrangements%20near%20the%20defence%20airport%20to%20receive%20the%20dignitaries%20coming%20for%20the%20pre-wedding%20event%2C%20added%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20past%20November%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20appealed%20to%20rich%20Indians%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-narendra-modi-urges-rich-families-shun-weddings-abroad-hold-them-in-india%2Farticleshow%2F105509867.cms%5C%22%3Ewed%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20Maan%20Ki%20Baat%20radio%20speech.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20yet%20whether%20that%20appeal%20coincided%20with%20the%20special%20preparations%20that%20his%20government%20was%20carrying%20out%20at%20the%20Jamnagar%20defence%20airport%20for%20the%20Ambani%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambani%20scion%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20was%20held%20at%20a%20temple%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20December%2029.%20News%20reports%20had%20then%20said%20the%20wedding%20would%20take%20place%20in%20Jamnagar%20on%20March%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20business%20daily%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20carried%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcompany%2Fcorporate-trends%2Fanant-radhika-wedding-will-kick-off-wed-in-india-economy%2Farticleshow%2F108113840.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20February%2029%20with%20the%20headline%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnant-Radhika%20wedding%20will%20kick-off%20%E2%80%98wed%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20Economy%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20yet%20if%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20special%20arrangements%20at%20the%20Jamnagar%20airport%20was%20due%20to%20a%20new%20policy%20adopted%20for%20all%20to%20augment%20the%20%E2%80%98wed-in%20India%E2%80%99%20economy%20mooted%20by%20Modi%2C%20or%20it%20was%20a%20one-off%20gesture%20towards%20the%20Ambani%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20in%20May%202023%2C%20South%20Africa%20was%20rocked%20by%20the%20news%20of%20a%20special%20charter%20flight%20carrying%20guests%20from%20India%20for%20the%20wedding%20of%20the%20son%20of%20an%20Indian-origin%20billionaire%20business%20tycoon%20seen%20close%20to%20former%20President%20Jacob%20Zuma%2C%20allowed%20by%20the%20government%20to%20land%20at%20a%20defence%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industrialists%20Atul%2C%20Ajay%20and%20Rajesh%20Guptas%20were%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20benefactors%20of%20Zuma%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20the%20African%20National%20Congress%20(ANC).%20News%20reports%20had%20then%20said%20the%20guests%20included%20Bollywood%20stars%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20BBC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-22386704%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20escorted%20the%20guests%20to%20the%20casino%20resort%20of%20Sun%20City%20for%20the%20wedding%20of%2023-year-old%20Vega%20Gupta%2C%20the%20Gupta%20brothers%E2%80%99%20niece%2C%20to%20Indian-born%20Aaskash%20Jahajgarhia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20South%20African%20and%20international%20Press%20highlighting%20the%20%E2%80%98political%20scandal%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20then%20ruling%20ANC%20government%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20African%20National%20Congress%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20concern%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20shall%20never%20allow%20a%20situation%20where%20our%20ports%20of%20entry%20and%20National%20Key%20Points%20are%20penetrated%20with%20impunity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20African%20minister%20in%20the%20Presidency%20Collins%20Chabane%20told%20reporters%20that%20an%20investigation%20had%20been%20ordered%20and%20it%20would%20also%20%E2%80%9Cunearth%20whether%20diplomatic%20privilege%20had%20been%20abused%20(by%20the%20Indian%20embassy)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20African%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20chief%20of%20protocol%20Bruce%20Koloane%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontroversy-over-use-of-airport-by-gupta-familys-wedding-guests-520925%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately%20for%20allowing%20the%20Waterklof%20Air%20Force%20Base%20airport%20near%20Pretoria%20to%20be%20used%20by%20the%20Guptas%20pending%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709362992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F02122914%2FUntitled-design-22.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsensitive-defence-airport-in-jamnagar-gets-international-tag-for-anant-ambanis-wedding-bash%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20international%20tag%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20airport%2C%20which%20is%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20border%2C%20was%20given%20for%20February%2025%20to%20March%205%2C%20so%20that%20guests%20invited%20to%20the%20wedding%20can%20land%20close%20to%20the%20venue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsensitive-defence-airport-in-jamnagar-gets-international-tag-for-anant-ambanis-wedding-bash%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Victoria%20Beckham's%20Paris%20fashion%20show%20disrupted%20by%20animal%20rights%20protesters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709362020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com