a%20Janata%20Party%20government.%20The%20documentary%20should%20have%20been%20screened%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%201%2C%20at%20the%2015th%20edition%20of%20the%20BIFFes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20movies%20to%20be%20screened%20are%20cleared%20by%20the%20I%26amp%3BB%20ministry.%20However%2C%20the%20ministry%20did%20not%20give%20a%20green%20signal%20to%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Satyagraha%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%20The%20Central%20authorities%20have%20told%20us%20that%20the%20matter%20pictured%20in%20the%20documentary%20is%20a%20sensitive%20subject%20and%20hence%20it%20should%20be%20withheld%20from%20being%20screened%20at%20the%20film%20festival.%20Following%20the%20instructions%2C%20we%20have%20withdrawn%20the%20screening%20of%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Satyagraha%E2%80%99.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20scheduled%20for%20screening%20on%20Friday%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20G.%20Himanth%20Raju%2C%20registrar%2C%20Karnataka%20Chalanchithra%20Academy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fdocumentary-on-2020-21-farmers-stir-barred-from-bengaluru-film-fest%2Farticleshow%2F108149376.cms%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20I%26amp%3BB%20ministry%20also%20refused%20permission%20to%20a%20documentary%20on%20Israel%20and%20also%20on%20Ukraine%20(20%20days%20in%20Mariupol).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20now%20the%2086-minute-long%20documentary%20on%20farmers%20had%20been%20screened%20offline%20at%20certain%20forums%20including%20four%20international%20film%20festivals.%20Kisan%20Satyagraha%20won%20the%20award%20for%20best%20Indian%20documentary%20at%20the%20White%20Unicorn%20International%20Film%20Festival%202022%20and%20emerged%20as%20a%20finalist%20at%20the%20Anatolia%20International%20Film%20Festival%202022%20apart%20from%20being%20selected%20for%20two%20more%20film%20festivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709358760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.t