loss%20of%20lives%20in%20Northern%20Gaza%20yesterday%20during%20the%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance.%20Such%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20and%20the%20larger%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20cause%20for%20extreme%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20100%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20were%20killed%20on%20Thursday%20as%20crowds%2C%20starving%20and%20desperate%20for%20food%2C%20gathered%20around%20aid%20trucks%2C%20with%20Israeli%20troops%20opening%20fire.%20The%20United%20Nations%20had%20told%20the%20Security%20Council%20two%20days%20ago%20that%20the%20famine%20in%20Gaza%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146997%5C%22%3Ealmost%20inevitable%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20at%20least%20576%2C000%20people%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfacing%20catastrophic%20levels%20of%20deprivation%20and%20starvation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20military%20claimed%20that%20soldiers%20only%20fired%20at%20a%20small%20group%20that%20swarmed%20a%20checkpoint%20and%20that%20the%20rest%20had%20died%20due%20to%20stampede.%20However%2C%20witnesses%20told%20western%20media%20agencies%20that%20crowds%20around%20the%20food%20trucks%20were%20hit%20by%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20acting%20director%20al-Awda%20hospital%2C%20Mohammad%20Salha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2Fgaza-doctor-gunfire-accounted-80-wounds-hospital-aid-107715222%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20out%20of%20the%20176%20injured%20treated%2C%20142%20had%20received%20gunshot%20wounds.%20As%20per%20Health%20officials%2C%20at%20least%20112%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20750%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20action%20began%20after%20Hamas%20launched%20attacks%20into%20Israel%20that%20killed%20more%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C200%20people%2C%20with%20240%20others%20taken%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20toll%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20five-month-long%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%20now%20stands%20at%20over%2030%2C000%2C%20with%20more%20than%2071%2C000%20wounded.%20The%20US%20secretary%20of%20defence%20Lloyd%20Austin%20said%20at%20a%20Congressional%20hearing%20that%20around%2025%2C000%20women%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20backlash%20from%20European%20capitals%20after%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20killing%20has%20been%20sharp%2C%20with%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20squarely%20blaming%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeep%20indignation%20at%20the%20images%20coming%20from%20Gaza%20where%20civilians%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers.%20I%20express%20my%20strongest%20condemnation%20of%20these%20shootings%20and%20call%20for%20truth%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20respect%20for%20international%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEmmanuelMacron%2Fstatus%2F1763354898119229476%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20demanded%20that%20a%20ceasefire%20must%20be%20immediately%20implemented%20to%20allow%20distribution%20of%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20foreign%20minister%20St%C3%A9phane%20S%C3%A9journ%C3%A9%20called%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Flive%2F2024%2Fmar%2F01%2Fgaza-aid-convoy-deaths-israel-middle-east-crisis-live-latest-news%3Fpage%3Dwith%253Ablock-65e195bc8f08a1a184508922%23block-65e195bc8f08a1a184508922%5C%22%3Eindependent%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CFrance%20calls%20things%20by%20their%20name.%20This%20applies%20when%20we%20designate%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group%2C%20but%20we%20must%20also%20call%20things%20by%20their%20name%20when%20there%20are%20atrocities%20in%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20s