dia%20did%20not%20have%20much%20choice%20but%20to%20issue%20a%20condemnatory%20statement%2C%20even%20though%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20name%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20deaths%20or%20cite%20Israel%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20simply%20tweeted%20that%20India%20was%20in%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20explosion%20in%20a%20Gaza%20hospital%20killed%20hundreds%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20the%20Indian%20PM%20for%20the%20first%20time%20during%20this%20current%20conflict%20reiterated%20that%20New%20Delhi%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%5C%22%3Etraditionally%20supported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3Eabstained%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20voting%20on%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20that%20called%20for%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20violence%20in%20Gaza.%20Less%20than%20two%20months%20later%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-votes-in-favour-of-unga-resolution-calling-for-immediate-ceasefire-in-gaza%5C%22%3Evoted%20in%20favour%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20new%20resolution%20adopted%20by%20UNGA%20that%20called%20for%20an%20urgent%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709315293000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28144318%2Fhumanitarian-aid-to-gaza-e1701163097133.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdeeply-shocked-india-on-palestinians-killed-during-delivery-of-humanitarian-aid%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20100%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20were%20killed%20on%20T