n%20who%20was%2010%20years%20older%20than%20me.%20At%20my%20%3Cem%3Ehaldi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eceremony%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20team%20from%20the%20NGO%20came%20to%20my%20rescue%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%2C%20my%20marriage%20was%20stopped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Pune%20and%20continued%20my%20higher%20studies%20till%20class%2012%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20in%20a%20bank.%20Whatever%20I%20am%20today%20is%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20this%20NGO%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20long-term%20impact%20post-handholding%2C%20Manjusha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20we%20organised%20an%20alumni%20meet%20of%20our%20200%20students.%20It%20was%20really%20overwhelming%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20how%20these%20children%20are%20doing%20well%20in%20their%20lives.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20working%20with%20multinational%20companies%2C%20some%20of%20them%20have%20become%20principals%20of%20schools%2C%20and%20some%20are%20working%20at%20the%20construction%20site%2C%20but%20as%20civil%20engineers%20and%20not%20as%20labourers.%20The%20impact%20motivates%20us%20to%20keep%20on%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Manjusha%20Doshi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709218222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20belief%20that%20every%20child%20has%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20education%2C%20health%20care%2C%20and%20a%20secure%20future%2C%20Tara%20Mobile%20Creches%20Pune%20has%20been%20working%20for%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20children%20of%20migrant%20families.%20With%20its%20mobile%20cr%C3%A8ches%2C%20it%20has%20catered%20to%201%20lakh%20such%20kids.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343596%2Fdaycare-in-pune-for-migrant-kids-tara-mobile-creches-pune-jobs-for-kids-of-migrant-workers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Launches%20Free%20Online%20Course%20on%20Remote%20Sensing%20to%20Help%20Students%20Learn%20New%20Tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Remote%20Sensing%20(IIRS)%2C%20an%20institute%20under%20ISRO%2C%20is%20offering%20a%20free%20training%20programme%20in%20remote%20sensing%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20aims%20to%20help%20students%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20remote%20sensing%20technology%20and%20its%20applications%20in%20geological%20analysis%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F108420%2Fbarren-island-india-only-active-volcano-andaman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploration%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EScience%20post-graduates%20specialising%20in%20earth%20sciences%20or%20related%20fields%3B%20BTech%20graduates%20in%20civil%20engineering%2C%20geoscience%2C%20or%20mining%20engineering%3B%20and%20scientific%20staff%2C%20faculty%20and%20researchers%20of%20Central%2FState%20Government%20universities%20and%20institutions%20may%20apply.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20course%20will%20deal%20with%20multifaceted%20applications%20of%20remote%20sensing%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337390%2Fbest-frozen-lakes-in-india-snowfall-winter-travel-destinations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeological%20sciences%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20mapping%2C%20monitoring%2C%20and%20characterisation%20of%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20have%20knowledge%20of%20the%20basics%20of%20remote%20sensing%20and%20GIS%20(geographic%20information%20system).%3C%2Fli%3E%