This%20is%20because%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20spectrum%20of%20things%20which%20we%20perceive%20as%20normal%2C%20but%20are%20inaccessible%20to%20blind%20persons.%20But%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20textures%20played%20a%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Giulia%2C%20who%20shares%20what%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceducative%20experience%E2%80%9D%20it%20has%20been%20for%20all%20the%20individuals%20involved%20in%20the%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20required%20us%20to%20ask%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20and%20really%20break%20through%20what%20we%20knew%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20person%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Project%20Sparsh%20testifies%20that%20it%20reaffirmed%20the%20belief%20that%20art%20is%20a%20universal%20language%2C%20speaking%20to%20each%20individual%E2%80%99s%20senses%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709215793000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343534%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sparsh%2C%20an%20initiative%20by%20Asian%20Paints%20and%20St%2Bart%20Foundation%2C%20is%20transforming%20Jaipur%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthan%20Netraheen%20Kalyan%20Sangh%20Institute%20into%20a%20place%20where%20visually%20impaired%20children%20can%20appreciate%20art.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343534%2Fsparsh-asian-paints-start-foundation-initiative-tactile-art-rajasthan-netraheen-kalyan-sangh-jaipur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ticket%20Collector%20to%20UPSC%20Officer%20to%20Shark%20Tank%3A%20Founder%20Won%20Rs%2045%20Lakh%20for%20Anti-Theft%20Luggage%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20us%20know%20someone%20who%20has%20lost%20a%20wallet%20or%20a%20bag%20during%20our%20travels.%20It%20might%20be%20because%20they%20left%20it%20or%20it%20got%20stolen.%20Pickpocketing%20and%20luggage%20theft%20cases%20are%20unfortunately%20a%20common%20occurrence%20while%20commuting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20case%20of%20pickpocketing%20made%20Atul%20Gupta%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Arista%20Vault%20rethink%20the%20way%20people%20look%20at%20travel%20safety.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20my%20wallet%20stolen%20on%20the%20Delhi%20metro%20and%20was%20technically%20stranded%20with%20no%20money%20on%20my%20way%20to%20an%20important%20event.%20This%20triggered%20a%20thought%20and%20I%20started%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas%20on%20how%20we%20can%20make%20travelling%20safer%20using%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-founded%20by%20Atul%20and%20Purvi%20Roy%2C%20the%20startup%20makes%20products%20that%20make%20our%20travel%20safer.%20From%20smart%20wallets%20to%20luggage%2C%20it%20has%20made%20travelling%20safer%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20duo%20won%20the%20sharks%20over%20at%20the%20TV%20show%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20and%20won%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2045%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20Unique%20Journey%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20unique%20products%2C%20what%20is%20interesting%20is%20the%20journey%20the%20founders%20had%20before%20collaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2039%2C%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20career%20started%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20my%20batch%20to%20clear%20the%20Railways%20exams%20and%20got%20posted%20as%20a%20ticket%20collector.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20lost%20their%20luggage%20to%20theft.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20distress%20and%20loss%20it%20caused%20to%20the%20people%20and%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259714%2Fwest-bengal-history-woman-bela-mitra-brave-india-freedom-struggle-british-raj%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20the%20railways%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Atul%20also%20started%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20to%20become%20a%20government%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20managing%20both%20things%20and%20I%20failed%20four%20times%20before%20cracking%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20served%20as%20an%20officer%2C%20conducting%20audits%20of%20national%20Navratna%20companies%20and%20Maharatna%20PSUs%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20This%20marked%20around%2013-14%20years%20into%20my%20service.%20While%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20servant%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20yearned%20to%20create%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20has%20launched%20smart%20wallet%20which%20anti-theft%20and%20enables%20you%20to%20track%20its%20location.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-768x402.