ing%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20artist%2C%20I%20look%20for%20happiness%20in%20my%20work%3B%20the%20food%20I%20taste%2C%20and%20the%20people%20I%20meet.%20If%20I%20look%20back%20at%20the%20graph%20of%20my%20happiness%20over%20the%20years%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20constant.%20The%20little%20things%20made%20me%20happy%20when%20I%20started%20and%20they%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20while%20Maroof%20has%20found%20fame%20in%20diligently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338686%2Ffreedom-fighter-gandhian-india-best-railway-minister-madhu-dandavate-rail-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchiving%20India%E2%80%99s%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20was%20never%20the%20original%20plan%2C%20he%20shares.%20Months%20into%20a%20commerce%20course%2C%20he%20figured%20the%20traditional%20academic%20route%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20him%20and%20he%20dropped%20out%20to%20start%20a%20design%20agency%20in%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20visual%20arts%20had%20always%20intrigued%20me.%20I%E2%80%99d%20always%20viewed%20the%20world%20from%20a%20different%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20agency%20was%20on%20its%20feet%2C%20Maroof%20says%20there%20was%20a%20deeper%20calling%20he%20had.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20explore%20my%20city%20and%20tell%20the%20stories%20it%20held%20within%20its%20walls.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202048px)%20100vw%2C%202048px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maroof%20Umar%20is%20a%20heritage%20storyteller%20who%20chronicles%20the%20history%20and%20culture%20of%20Lucknow%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t