dia%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20were%20three%20major%20events%20which%20would%20take%20Sarah%20to%20where%20she%20is%20today.%20Around%20a%20decade%20back%20on%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve%2C%20they%20were%20living%20on%20Harrington%20Road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20just%20watched%20the%20movie%20PK.%20Like%20Aamir%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20alien%20character%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20this%20puppy%20just%20appeared%20in%20our%20lives%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20We%20heard%20a%20dog%20crying%20but%20assumed%20that%20someone%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20had%20just%20brought%20a%20young%20pup%20who%20was%20crying.%20But%20by%208%20pm%2C%20however%2C%20I%20felt%20something%20was%20wrong.%20So%2C%20I%20stepped%20out%20of%20our%20home%20and%20finally%20found%20this%20black%20and%20white%20puppy%20wedged%20between%20a%20parked%20car%20and%20the%20wall%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20initial%20attempts%20at%20pulling%20this%20puppy%20out%20weren%E2%80%99t%20successful.%20Though%20injured%2C%20he%20was%20feisty%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20touch%20him.%20Gerry%20finally%20managed%20to%20pull%20this%20pup%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20vet%20on%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve.%20We%20eventually%20found%20one%20but%20had%20to%20pay%20five%20times%20the%20rate%20to%20get%20them%20over%20to%20our%20locality%20and%20give%20it%20first%20aid.%20On%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20all%20clinics%20were%20shut.%20We%20could%20only%20take%20PK%20for%20treatment%20on%20the%202nd%20(of%20January).%C2%A0Having%20a%20spinal%20compression%20and%20a%20broken%20leg%2C%20PK%20was%20paralysed.%20After%20much%20care%2C%20attention%20and%20physiotherapy%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month%2C%20PK%20started%20walking%2C%20running%20and%20playing.%20Although%20we%20were%20initially%20reluctant%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20adopt%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-