ase%20shade%20cloth%20for%20your%20garden.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGardening%20blogger%20Harith%20Tharang%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9COld%20sheets%2C%20old%20window%20screens%2C%20or%20narrow%20panels%20of%20wood%20lattice%20can%20all%20effectively%20cover%20and%20cool%20the%20plants%20in%20your%20garden.%20However%2C%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20cover%20is%20kept%20at%20least%20several%20inches%20above%20the%20plants.%20If%20using%20a%20cloth%20cover%2C%20staple%20each%20end%20to%20stakes%20placed%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20garden.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20mindful%20of%20the%20changing%20position%20of%20the%20sun%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126518%2Flittle-known-leafy-green-vegetables-india-need-try%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20adjust%20shade%20%3C%2Fa%3Estructures%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Upgrade%20the%20soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpgrading%20your%20soil%20for%20the%20summer%20season%20is%20crucial%20to%20ensure%20that%20your%20plants%20have%20the%20nutrients%2C%20moisture%20retention%2C%20and%20drainage%20they%20need%20to%20thrive%20in%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20gardening%20website%3Cem%3E%20indiagardening.com%3C%2Fem%3E%20suggests%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20early%20summers%2C%20amend%20the%20garden%20soil%20to%20enhance%20the%20water%20retaining%20capability%20as%20well%20as%20aeration.%20Use%20organic%20matter%20or%20compost%20as%20it%20improves%20water%20retention%20and%20is%20also%20beneficial%20for%20microbes%20and%20worms%20in%20the%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20to%20prune%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETimely%20pruning%20your%20garden%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way.%20Remove%20dead%20or%20diseased%20foliage%2C%20and%20prune%20back%20overgrown%20bra